title: 'Putin's terrorâ€™: Russian Kalibr Cruise missiles pound U.S. arms depot in Ukraine's Ternopil
description: Just a week after warning the West against sending longer-range missiles to Ukraine to help it defend Russia, Vladimir Putin has found his 'new target' in the war-torn nation. The Russian Defence Ministry has released a video showing its Black Sea Frigate firing four Kalibr Cruise missiles and destroying a U.S. and European arms depot in Ukraine's Ternopil region. Ukraine has claimed that the strike injured 22 people including a 12-year-old. Ukraine's President Volodymyr Zelensky has hit back at his Russian counterpart claiming that Russia's aim with 'senseless missile strike' was only to spread 'terror'. Zelensky also appealed to the West yet again and made a case on why Ukraine should be provided longer-range missiles at the earliest. Watch this video for more details.|#russia #ukraine #kalibr #cruisemissile #ternopil #arms #warehouse #russiaukrainewar #russiaukraineconflict #vladimirputin #volodymyrzelensky #volodymyrzelenskyy #zelenskiy #putin #joebiden #biden #zelensky #zelenskyy

title: Kuwait To Deport Expats Over Protest Against Prophet Remarks
description: Kuwait has said that it will deport expatriates who participated in a demonstration against the remarks made by suspended BJP spokesperson Nupur Sharma on Prophet Muhammad, news agency ANI reported quoting local media. The decision was taken as the protesters violated the laws and regulations of the country which prohibits sit-ins or demonstrations by expatriates in Kuwait, the report said.|About NDTV: NDTV brings you unbiased and comprehensive coverage of news and entertainment programmes in India and abroad. title: Putin signals control in Occupied Ukraine: Melitopol residents get Russian passports
description: For this first time since over 100 days of war in Ukraine, Russia has handed over its passports to a select few citizens from Ukraine who had asked for them. Marking Russia Day celebrations in several occupied cities of east and south Ukraine, Moscow-backed officials handed over passports to Ukrainians in Melitopol city. Russian flags were raised in some cities while bands played at concert in some other parts of Ukraine to mark Russia Day. Celebrations were also reportedly held in Mariupol, Kherson and Zaporizhzhia. As per media reports in Ukraine, several locals avoided these celebrations amid war. Watch this video for more details.|#russia #ukraine #passport #russiaukraineconflict #russiaukrainewar #melitopol #mariupol #kherson #zaporizhzhia #russiaday

title: Cerita Nenek Eril Doanya Terkabul hingga Titipan Kain Kafan Untuk Eril
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV  Setelah acara prosesi pemakaman selesai, Ridwan Kamil mempersilakan ibunya Tjutju Sukaesih yang juga nenek dari Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz menyampaikan kata. ||||Tjutju menceritakan isi doanya yang dijawab oleh Allah SWT. ||||Ia sempat berdoa agar cucunya Eril yang hilang di sungai Aare bisa muncul ke permukaan.||||"Alhamdulillah ya Allah. Saya mengharapkan dan mendoakan Eril bisa muncul ke permukaan karena dia lahir di benua Amerika dan kejadian ini adalah di benua Eropa, dan takdirnya seperti yang kita saksikan. Tapi saya mohon, saya bilang, bisa dikuburkan di negeri benua Asia dan di Indonesia khususnya," ucap Tjutju.||||Baca Juga Momen Atalia Peluk Zahra di Pemakaman Eril di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298500/momen-atalia-peluk-zahra-di-pemakaman-eril||||Nenek Eril itu juga bersyukur kini menyaksikan pemakaman sang cucu di Cimaung. ||||"Sekarang kita saksikan di Cimaung ini, tempat Eril dikuburkan. Dan kita doakan semuanya, dan itulah saya ingin sampaikan bahwa doa saya terkabul," katanya.||||Lebih lanjut Tjutju juga bercerita saat Ridwan Kamil ke Swiss ia juga menitipkan kain kafan untuk Eril. ||||"Saya telah menitipkan kain kafan kepada anak saya pada saat di Swiss untuk mengkafani beliau. Alhamdulillah, pelajaran bagi saya, neneknya bahwa saya belum tentu seperti yang Eril lakukan, mohon doanya saja semoga kita semua belajar dari apa yang Eril lakukan dan anak saya Ridwan Kamil dijadikan pemimpin yang adil menurut Engkau ya Allah dan bukan adil menurut manusia," ucapnya.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298507/cerita-nenek-eril-doanya-terkabul-hingga-titipan-kain-kafan-untuk-eril

title: Russia 'used cluster munitions' in Ukrainian city of Kharkiv - BBC News
description: Russia has killed hundreds of civilians in Ukraine's second largest city, Kharkiv, using indiscriminate shelling and widely banned cluster munitions, according to new research by Amnesty International.|Amnesty says it has found evidence of Russian forces repeatedly using cluster bombs, as well as "scatterable" munitions - rockets that eject smaller mines that explode later at timed intervals.| Russia has previously denied using cluster munitions in Ukraine and insisted that Russian forces have only struck military targets.|The BBC visited five separate impact sites in residential neighbourhoods in Kharkiv and saw evidence of a distinctive, symmetrical spalling effect associated with cluster munitions.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#BBCNews

title: Momen Atalia Peluk Zahra di Pemakaman Eril
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV  Ibunda Eril, Atalia Praratya memeluk putri mereka, Camillia Laetitia Azzahra atau Zahra saat petugas tengah menimbun tanah pemakaman. ||||Keduanya sama-sama saling menguatkan satu sama lain.||||Momen tersebut saat keduanya duduk di dekat makam Eril di Cimaung, Bandung, Jawa Barat.||||Sebelumnya Zahra juga sempat ikut turun ke sungai Aare bersama kakaknya Emmeril dan salah seorang teman.||||Baca Juga Ganjar Ungkap Sesuatu Ekspresi dari Ridwan Kamil Saat Bertakziah Jenazah Eril di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298362/ganjar-ungkap-sesuatu-ekspresi-dari-ridwan-kamil-saat-bertakziah-jenazah-eril||||Saat kejadian darurat warga bernama Heinrich sempat menyelamatkan teman Zahra dan Eril untuk naik ke daratan.||||Sebelumnya Emmeril dinyatakan hilang di sungai Aare pada Kamis (26/5/2022). ||||Jasadnya ditemukan 2 pekan kemudian pada Rabu (8/6/2022). ||||KBRI Bern membantu pemulangan jenazah Eril hingga tiba di tanah air pada Minggu (12/6/2022). ||||Ribuan pelayat pun memenuhi lokasi pemakaman Eril sebagai respons empati dan simpati untuk almarhum dan keluarga Ridwan Kamil.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298500/momen-atalia-peluk-zahra-di-pemakaman-eril
tags: adik eril|atalia praratya|emmeril kahn mumtadz|pemakaman eril|zahra

title: Ridwan Kamil Menahan Tangis di Pemakaman Eril: Izinkan Kami Menyesuaikan Diri, Beradaptasi
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS TV  Ridwan Kamil menutup rangkaian prosesi pemakaman Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril dengan permintaan maaf dan terima kasih.||||Ia meminta maaf pada masyarakat luas jika ada hal-hal yang tidak berkenan, selama belasan hari sejak pencarian Eril di Sungai Aare.||||"Mohon maaf kalau selama 12 hari adalah hal-hal yang kurang berkenan, ada hal-hal yang tidak nyaman, semata-mata kami berusaha berikhtiar sebaik-baiknya sambil kita berdoa," ujar Ridwan Kamil setelah pemakaman Eril, Senin (13/6).||||Baca Juga Penampakan Nisan Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz, hingga Keluarga Tabur Bunga di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298512/penampakan-nisan-emmeril-kahn-mumtadz-hingga-keluarga-tabur-bunga||||"Eril pasti sangat bahagia dan pasti sudah tenang dan kami sebagai orangtua sudah sangat iklas sangat tenang," lanjutnya.||||RIdwan Kamil juga memohon maaf atas ketidaknyamanan warga khususnya di jalan, ketika iring-iringan jenazah dan warga padati jalan menuju tempat pemakaman Eril.||||Ia menyebut bahwa antusiasme warga mengantar Eril ke peristirahatan terakhir tak bisa dihindari.||||"Saya memohon maaf hari ini jika di prosesi pemakaman membuat masyarakat kurang nyaman di perjalanan, kami mohon maaf tidak bermaksud, antusiasme warga tidak bisa kita hindari," ucap Ridwan Kamil.||||Ridwan Kamil, Atalia, dan Zara meminta waktu untuk menyesuaikan diri usai duka yang mereka alami.||||Kang Emil juga berterima kasih pada masyrakat luas yang telah menjaga privasi keluarganya selama proses pencarian Eril hingga pemakaman Eril.||||"Mudahan-mudahan kebaikan kawan-kawan semua yang sangat menghormati privasi kami selama 14 hari saya ucvapkan terima kasih," ucapnya.||||"Kali ini izinkan kami menyesuaikan diri, beradaptasi terhadap situasi duka yang sedang kami alami."||||Video Editor: Agung Ramdani||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298548/ridwan-kamil-menahan-tangis-di-pemakaman-eril-izinkan-kami-menyesuaikan-diri-beradaptasi

title: Sambil Menahan Tangis, Ridwan Kamil : Terima Kasih Telah Menghormati Privasi Kami
description: CIMAUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Dalam perjalanan meninggalkan lokasi pemakaman, Ridwan Kamil mengucapkan terima kasih kepada Presiden, Wakil Presiden, para menteri, dan pihak kepolisian yang membantu proses pencarian Eril.||||Ridwan Kamil juga meminta maaf jika selama masa penacarian dalam 14 hari ini ada hal yang tidak berkenan.||||Ia telah merasa ikhlas dan tenang karena Eril sudah dimakamkan dengan cara yang baik dan dibanjiri doa-doa dari seluruh Indonesia.||||Baca Juga Dikenal Sebagai Pendiri Jaber Zilenial, Eril Selalu Sebarkan Kebaikan Pada Sesama di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298475/dikenal-sebagai-pendiri-jaber-zilenial-eril-selalu-sebarkan-kebaikan-pada-sesama||||Ridwan Kamil juga minta maaf atas kepadatan yang terjadi hari di Bandung.||||Sambil menahan tangis, Ridwan Kamil mengucapkan terima kasih yang sebesar-sebesarnya karena telah menghormati privasinya dan keluarga.||||Ridwan Kamil mengatakan nanti akan ada waktunya untuk bercerita lebih banyak soal pencarian Eril selama 14 hari ini.||||Untuk saat ini Ridwan Kamil dan keluarga masih dalam masa berkabung dan penyesuaian diri.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298487/sambil-menahan-tangis-ridwan-kamil-terima-kasih-telah-menghormati-privasi-kami

title: [Full] Prosesi Pemakaman Anak Ridwan Kamil Eril di Cimaung Bandung
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV  Anak Ridwan Kamil Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril dimakamkan di kawasan pemakaman Yayasan Islami Centre Baitul Ridwan.||||Eril dimakamkan pada Senin, 13 Juni 2022.||||Makam Eril berada di sebelah sungai kecil dengan pemandangan gunung dan pesawahan.||||Baca Juga Jenazah Eril Dimasukkan ke Liang Lahad Diiringi Lantunan Ayat Suci Al-quran di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298431/jenazah-eril-dimasukkan-ke-liang-lahad-diiringi-lantunan-ayat-suci-al-quran||||Makam Eril berada di sebelah masjid yang akan dibangun yang dinamai seperti nama Eril yaitu Masjid Al-Mumtadz.||||Eril dimakamkan setelah disemayamkan di Gedung Pakuan, Bandung pada 12 Juni 2022.||||Sejumlah tokoh dan masyarakat berdatangan untuk bertakziah, menyolatkan jenazah dan berdoa untuk Eril.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Krisna Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298433/full-prosesi-pemakaman-anak-ridwan-kamil-eril-di-cimaung-bandung

title: Prabowo, Ganjar, Anies, Siapa yang Paling Menarik Perhatian? | Rosi
description: KOMPASTV - Nama Prabowo Subianto, Ganjar Pranowo dan Anies Baswedan kerap menduduki peringkat teratas dalam berbagai survei elektabilitas capres 2024. Menurut Direktur Eksekutif Indo Barometer, M. Qodari, dari ketiga nama tersebut yang paling berpeluang untuk maju di Pemilu 2024 adalah Ketua Umum Partai Gerindra, Prabowo Subianto yang sudah "paket lengkap".||||Qodari juga mengingatkan sepopuler apapun kandidat capres, dia tidak bisa maju tanpa dukungan partai politik. Apa saja paket lengkap yang dimiliki seorang Prabowo Subianto? Dan bagaimana peluang nama-nama lainnya di Pemilu 2024?||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298514/prabowo-ganjar-anies-siapa-yang-paling-menarik-perhatian-rosi

title: Spicy Lal Chutni Qeema Calzone Recipe By Food Fusion
description: Spicy Lal Chutni Qeema Calzone a spice up fusion with a desi touch to the calzone we all love. #HappyCookingToYou #FoodFusion |Written Recipe: https://bit.ly/3xIyiyO|Ingredients:|Prepare Dough:|-Doodh (Milk) lukewarm Â¾ Cup|-Khameer (Instant yeast) 2 tsp|-Bareek cheeni (Caster sugar) 1 tbs|-Maida (All-purpose flour) sifted 3 Cups|-Namak (Salt) 1 tsp|-Cooking oil 2 tsp|-Lukewarm water Â½ Cup or as required |-Cooking oil 1 tsp |Prepare Lal Mirch Chutni Qeema Filling:|-Kashmiri lal mirch (Kashmiri red chillies) soaked 6-8|-Lehsan (Garlic) 8-10 cloves |-Sukhi lal mirch (Dried red chillies) 4-5|-Mong phali (Peanuts) roasted 3 tbs|-Namak (Salt) Â¼ tsp or to taste |-Sabut dhania (Coriander seeds) 1 tsp|-Zeera (Cumin seeds) Â½ tsp|-Lemon juice 2 tbs|-Water Â½ Cup|-Cooking oil 4-5 tbs|-Pyaz (Onion) sliced 2-3 medium |-Beef qeema (Mince) Â½ kg|-Adrak lehsan paste (Ginger garlic paste) Â½ tbs|-Zeera powder (Cumin powder) 1 tsp|-Lal mirch powder (Red chilli powder) 1 tsp or to taste |-Namak (Salt) 1 tsp or to taste|-Garam masala powder Â½ tsp|-Dahi (Yogurt) hung 3 tbs|-Water Â¼ Cup or as required |-Hara dhania (Fresh coriander) chopped handful|-Water |-Doodh (Milk) |Directions:|Prepare Dough:|-In a small jug,add lukewarm milk,instant yeast,sugar & mix well,cover & let it rest for 5-10 minutes & set aside.|-In a bowl,dd all-purpose flour,salt,cooking oil & mix well until it crumbles.|-Add yeast mixture & mix well.|-Gradually add lukewarm water & knead until dough is formed. |-Grease with cooking oil,cover & let it proof for 1 hour (warm place).|Prepare Lal Mirch Chutni Qeema Filling:|-In a blender jug,add Kashmiri red chillies,garlic,dried red chillies,peanuts,salt,coriander seeds,cumin seeds,lemon juice,water and blend well to make a thick paste & set aside.|-In a pot,add cooking oil,onion & fry until light golden.|-Add beef mince & mix well until it changes color.|-Add ginger garlic paste,cumin powder,red chilli powder,salt,garam masala powder,mix well & cook for 2-3 minutes.|-Add yogurt,blended paste,mix well & cook for 4-5 minutes.|-Add water & mix well.|-Add fresh coriander & mix well,cover & cook on low flame for 8-10 minutes & set aside.|-Sprinkle dry flour and knead dough again until smooth.|-Take one portion (100g of dough),make a ball,sprinkle dry flour and roll out with the help of rolling pin.|-On baking try (greased with cooking oil and lined with butter paper),place rolled dough,on half side of the dough,add lal mirch chutni qeema filling,apply water and fold the other side over it,press and apply water and seal the edges.|-With the help of knife slightly add cuts on the surface and apply milk on top (makes 6). |-Bake in preheated oven at 200C for 25 minutes (on both grills).

title: Prophet Insult: Why Kuwait is deporting expats for protests against Nupur Sharma
description: The protests against suspended BJP leader Nupur Sharma and expelled BJP leader Naveen Jindal for their controversial remarks on Prophet, are costing expatriates in Kuwait dearly. As per Arab News, Kuwait administration is in the process of deporting these expats for violating the country's rules and regulations. Kuwaiti laws don't allow sit-ins or demonstrations by expats. As per news report, instructions have been issued to arrest expats from the Fahaheel area who organised a demonstration after Friday prayers in support of Prophet Muhammad. â€œThe detectives are in the process of arresting them and referring to the deportation center to be deported to their countries and will be banned from entering Kuwait again,â€ reported Al Rai, a Kuwaiti newspaper. title: China accuses India of 'acting provocatively' amid LAC standoff; Defence min absolves PLA's role
description: China shifts the blame on India for ongoing border standoff in the eastern Ladakh. Accusing India of acting provocatively, Chinese defence minister Wei Fenghe said that it's not the responsibility of Beijing to resolve for the standoff. New Delhi has consistently dismissed Beijingâ€™s allegations of acting provocatively since the standoff began in May 2020. The statement comes just days after External Affairs Minister S Jaishankar warned of response if China tries to alter the status quo at the borders. title: Russia solidifies its presence in Ukraine as Russian forces blow up a key bridge | English News

title: Mulia! Eril Sempat Sewakan Mobil Antik, Hasilnya Digunakan untuk Kegiatan Sosial
description: KOMPAS.TV - Semasa hidup Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz menyewakan mobil antik sebagai pekerjaan tambahan.||||Penghasilan tambahan Eril digunakan untuk berbagi dalam berbagai kegiatan sosial.||||Mobil antik ini kepunyaan Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz.||||Semasa hidup, mahasiswa Teknik Mesin Institut Teknologi Bandung ini punya kerjaan sampingan menyewakan mobil pengantin.||||Bekerja sama dengan sebuah Wedding Organizer di Bandung.||||Ayah Eril, Ridwan Kamil pun pernah promosi "Side Job" anaknya itu lewat instagram.||||Baca Juga Wali Kota Bogor hingga Bupati Bandung Datang ke Lokasi Pemakaman Eril di Cimaung di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298441/wali-kota-bogor-hingga-bupati-bandung-datang-ke-lokasi-pemakaman-eril-di-cimaung||||Setelah Eril berpulang, Ridwan Kamil bercerita jawabannya uang tambahan Eril untuk berbagai kegiatan sosial.||||"Mungkinkah ini pahala kesabaranmu saat tidak semua maumu kami berikan walau kami mampu, sehingga kamu harus bekerja sambilan sambil kuliah ril?"||||"Mungkinkah ini karena kebaikanmu membelikan baju lebaran kepada anak-anak yatim itu? atau karena kebaikanmu ngasih THR dari uangmu sendiri ke satpam-satpam itu Ril?."||||Sedianya bekal kebaikan Eril ini lah yang berbuah hantaran doa dan kasih dari banyak pihak di saat kepergiannya.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298447/mulia-eril-sempat-sewakan-mobil-antik-hasilnya-digunakan-untuk-kegiatan-sosial
tags: anak ridwan kamil|doa untuk eril|eril|eril kegiatan sosial|eril sewakan mobil antik|mobil antik eril

title: Detik-detik Peti Jenazah Eril Masuk Liang Kubur Disaksikan Ridwan Kamil dan Keluarga
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV  Inilah momen peti jenazah Eril dibawa petugas masuk ke liang lahat. ||||Pemakaman Eril berlangsung di kawasan Cimaung, dekat dengan Masjid yang memang dibangun oleh Ridwan Kamil. ||||Masjid tersebut pun diberi nama Al Mumtadz, seperti nama belakang Emmeril yang artinya terbaik. ||||Pada momen itu Ridwan Kamil yang pertama memasukkan tanah ke liang lahat lalu dilanjutkan oleh petugas. ||||Suasana khusyuk penuh khidmat ini berlangsung sejak keberangkatan jenazah Eril dari gedung Pakuan hingga tiba di lokasi pemakaman. ||||Baca Juga Ridwan Kamil dan Atalia Praratya Tegar saat Prosesi Pemakaman Eril di Cimaung di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298446/ridwan-kamil-dan-atalia-praratya-tegar-saat-prosesi-pemakaman-eril-di-cimaung||||Prosesi pemakaman disaksikan langsung oleh keluarga besar Ridwan Kamil. ||||Sedangkan untuk warga yang sudah berkumpul, dipersilakan ziarah setelah proses pemakaman selesai. ||||Jenazah Eril dikonfirmasi oleh kepolisian Swiss dan KBRI Bern pada Rabu (8/6/2022). ||||Eril ditemukan warga bernama Geraldine Beldi di bendungan Engehalde. ||||KBRI Bern pun turut membantu proses penyerahan jenazah ke pihak keluarga hingga jenazah Eril tiba di tanah air pada Minggu (12/6/2022). ||||Selamat jalan Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz. ||||Video Editor: Vila Randita|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298455/detik-detik-peti-jenazah-eril-masuk-liang-kubur-disaksikan-ridwan-kamil-dan-keluarga

title: China PLA member asks about role of Shangri-La Dialogue, if it's serving interest of US and allies
description: At the final plenary session of the Shangri-La Dialogue, a member of China's People's Liberation Army (PLA), Zhao Xiaozhuo, Senior Fellow, Academy of Military Sciences, PLA asked Singapore Defence Minister Ng Eng Hen and the chief executive of the International Institute for Strategic Studies John Chipman about the role of the security forum.|"There are negative views - views (of) the Shangri-la Dialogue as a forum dominated by the US and its allies, serving the interest of the US and its allies and also the topics discussed often point to differences, rather than cooperation, and divergence rather than convergence. So my question is: What role over the past years (has) Shangri-la Dialogue ... played in Asia Pacific security and how do you view the comments and opinions I have mentioned?" he said.|Said Dr Ng: "I've attended a number of conferences, I attended their Xiangshan Forum and sometimes, it's a matter of taste. I can imagine that people from the PLA come here and find this raucous a bit rambunctious. This is the Western liberal mode of many ideas. And from this, you're supposed to gain wisdom and they go back and say it was thoroughly discombobulating. That's entirely understandable."|He added: "On the other hand, when things are too structured, too predictable, people don't like to attend those, because they feel that it's too scripted, that when you say things, the end is already determined. So why not, not say it, just send me something and I can read it, rather than travel we know a few thousand miles and arrive to Singapore. For China it must decide for itself whether the Shangri La Dialogue adds value. There is no coercion for you to attend. Is it better? To come to an open platform, to subject yourself sometimes to the tyranny of questions and to what might seem a common view from others to explain yourself, or to retreat from that engagement? That is something that China must decide for itself."|"I think the People's Republic of China has benefitted hugely from the participation it has had in the Shangri-La Dialogue," said Dr Chipman, noting that there was a rare one-hour bilateral meeting between Chinese Defence Minister Wei Fenghe and US Defense Secretary Lloyd Austin. title: The 2023 Cadillac Escalade V Is A Bonkers Fast Big SUV With A Supercharged V8
description: For decades, the Cadillac brand has had two excellent sub-brands, the #Escalade and the V-Series high performance division. For 2023, the company is ready to combine the two with the first-ever #CadillacEscaladeV. This high-performance #EscaladeV adds a factory supercharger on top of the 6.2L V8 engine with enough boost to crank out 682 HP. Its also the first ever #Cadillac V-Series SUV which means that monster V8 comes with full-time AWD and a quick-shifting 10-speed AT. title: 'India under PM Modi canâ€™t be pressurized': Piyush Goyal hardens stand at WTO meet in Geneva
description: Union Commerce and Industry Minister Piyush Goyal has toughened India's stand at the 12th World Trade Organisation's ministerial meeting. He said that under the leadership of PM Modi, India has emerged as a global power and no one can pressure India to take decisions. Goyal further reiterated that the govt is committed to farmers and the poor of the country and their rights won't be violated. He also slammed the WTO & rich nations for not doing enough to tackle the crisis due to the Pandemic and rising food prices. Watch this video to know more.|#piyushgoyal  #unionminister #india  #worldtradeorganisation  #geneva  #farmers #wto #globalfood #foodcrisis  #atmanirbharbharat #narendramodi #pmmodi

title: [FULL] Pidato Ridwan Kamil Melepas Eril di Tempat Peristirahatan Terakhir
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV -  Jenazah Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz telah dimakamkan di Cimaung, Kabupaten Bandung pada Senin (13/6/2022). ||||Keluarga besar Ridwan Kamil dan Atalia menyaksikan momen jenazah Eril masuk ke liang kubur hingga petugas selesai menumpukkan tanah di kubur. ||||Hingga nisan terpasang, Ridwan Kamil pun sampaikan rasa terima kasih yang besar pada Presiden Jokow Widodo, Wapres Maruf Amin, hingga Forkompimda Jawa Barat atas perhatian hingga proses pemakaman ini berlangsung. ||||"Tidak ada satupun daun yang jatuh, atau ranting yang patah tanpa izin kehendak Allah. Atas nama kelaurga yang pertama menghaturkan terimakasih ke Presiden Jokowi, kepada Wapres KH Maruf Amin, kepada Forkopimda Jawa Barat Kab Bandung, kepada keluarga sanak saudara yang selalu hadir dan mendoakan, dan teman dan sahabat Eril, sahabat orang tuanya dan seluruh hadirin yang mendoakan,"ucap Ridwan Kamil di awal sambutannya. ||||Sebelumnya usai mendengar kabar Eril hilang di sungai Aare pada Kamis (26/5/2022), proses pencarian pun dimulai, dan Ridwan Kamil yang tengah berada di Inggris langsung bertolak ke Swiss. ||||Akhir dari pencarian selama 2 pekan jasad Eril akhirnya dikonfirmasi kepolisian Swiss usai ditemukan seorang warga Bern bernama Geraldine Beldi. ||||Ridwan Kamil pun kembali ke Swiss dan sempat memandikan dan mengumandangkan azan pada jasad Eril. ||||"Tentang hidup Eril rasanya terlalu singkat, tapi hidupnya singkat dan manfaat. Belum menghasilkan yang memadai tapi dicintai akbar. Hidup tidak lamanya hari tapi tiap hela nafas, dipakai buat berbuat baik. Kami mengikhlaskan eril pergi. Kami menyadari Allah mencukupkan kehidupannya. Mungkin berat kami tidak akan pernah melihat jasadnya untuk terakhir kali."ucap Ridwan Kamil mengenang Eril. ||||Untuknya dan keluarga, kehilangan Eril adalah kehilangan besar.||||Video Editor: Vila Randita|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298466/full-sambutan-ridwan-kamil-melepas-eril-di-tempat-peristirahatan-terakhir

description: Paris Jackson and Prince Jackson are celebrating their late father on Broadway's biggest night. title: Saat Zahra Sentuh Peti Jenazah Eril, Menatap Terdiam di Gedung Cargo Jenazah Bandara
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Inilah momen di saat putri Ridwan Kamil sekaligus adik Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril yaitu Camillia Laetitia Azzahra menyentuh peti jenazah kakaknya.||||Momen ini dibagikan pada Instagram story Ibunda, Atalia Praratya pada Senin, 13 Juni 2022.||||Zahra nampak sedih dan terdiam menatap peti jenazah Eril.||||Momen ini terjadi saat jenazah Eril tiba di Gedung Cargo Jenazah Bandara Soekarno Hatta pada Minggu, 12 Juni 2022 sore.||||Baca Juga Genggaman Erat Ridwan Kamil pada Atalia Praratya Saat Jenazah Eril Diturunkan dari Pesawat di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298374/genggaman-erat-ridwan-kamil-pada-atalia-praratya-saat-jenazah-eril-diturunkan-dari-pesawat||||Dalam momen ini pula terlihat Ridwan Kamil dan Atalia Praratya menguatkan Zahra atas kepergian Eril.||||Jenazah Eril dibawa dari Bandara Soekarno Hatta menuju Gedung Pakuan Bandung pada 12 Juni 2022 sore.||||Jenazah Eril dimakamkan pada Senin, 13 Juni 2022 pagi di Cimaung, Bandung, Jawa Barat.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Krisna Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298395/saat-zahra-sentuh-peti-jenazah-eril-menatap-terdiam-di-gedung-cargo-jenazah-bandara

title: Mahfud MD Datangi Sungai Aare Lihat Titik Lokasi Hilangnya Anak Ridwan Kamil Eril
description: BERN, KOMPAS.TV -  Menko Polhukam Mahfud MD di sela-sela kunjungan kerjanya di KBRI Bern, mendatangi Sungai Aare.||||Mahfud MD juga datangi titik lokasi hilangnya anak Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril.||||"Saya mau lihat sungainya," ujar Mahfud pada KOMPAS TV.||||Sungai Aare yang berlokasi di Bern itu merupakan lokasi tenggelamnya Emeril Mumtadz Khan alias Eril, putra Gubernur Bandung Ridwan Kamil yang jenazahnya dimakamkan hari ini, Senin (13/6).||||Baca Juga Sedih! Saat Nabila Ishma Bersimpuh di Peti Jenazah Eril, Bicarakan Sesuatu! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298418/sedih-saat-nabila-ishma-bersimpuh-di-peti-jenazah-eril-bicarakan-sesuatu||||Mahfud datang didampingi Duta Besar RI untuk Swiss, Muliaman Hadad bersama rombongan, guna mengumpulkan informasi.||||Dalam kesempatan itu, ia mengapresiasi kesigapan Kedutaan Besar RI (KBRI) atas penanganan kasus tenggelamnya Eril.||||"Menurut saya wajar, yang dilakukan (KBRI di Swiss, red) sudah maksimal, sesuai dengan fungsi dan prosedur. Begitu KBRI tahu ada peristiwa itu, KBRI langsung bertindak. Itu satu kecepatan yang menurut saya patut dihargai," ujar Mahfud.||||"Penjelasan KBRI untuk setiap perkembangan kasus cukup memberi informasi yang akurat, termasuk saat [Eril] ditemukan," imbuhnya.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298432/mahfud-md-datangi-sungai-aare-lihat-titik-lokasi-hilangnya-anak-ridwan-kamil-eril

description: The restaurant that launched McDonald's in Soviet Russia reopened over the weekend with a new name & logo. title: Sambutan RK Usai Prosesi Pemakaman Eril
description: Setelah prosesi pemakaman janazah putra sulungnya selesai, Ridwan Kamil menyampaikan bahwa keluarga besarnya mendapat banyak pelajaran dari musibah yang baru terjadi. Di antaranya adalah pelajaran tentang mengikhlaskan dan kembali meneruskan hidup.|Di dalam kenangan keluarga besar, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz adalah sosok yang sopan, soleh dan hangat. Hal serupa juga yang dikenang oleh teman-teman Eril.|"Tugas Eril di dunia telah selesai dengan baik. Mohon maaf jika semasa hidupnya ada ucapan dan tindakan Eril yang kurang berkenan. Kami mengucapkan terimakasih telah ikut mendoakan dan melepas kepergian Eril," tutup Ridwan Kamil di pemakaman keluarga di Cimaung, Bandung, Senin (13/6/2022) siang.|------------------|Ikuti juga media sosial METRO TV lainya agar dimanapun tetap terinfomasi dengan baik dan lengkap karena berita paling aktual kami sungguhkan  dan perkembangan terkini kami sampaikan.|METRO TV Official https://www.metrotvnews.com|METRO TV Official Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/metrotv|METRO TV Official Tiktok: https://www.tiktok.com/@metro_tv|METRO TV Facebook Fanpage: https://www.facebook.com/metrotv|METRO TV Official Twitter: https://twitter.com/metro_TV|#Metrotv #Beritaterkini #Beritaupdate

description: Subscribe to our YouTube channel for free here: |https://sc.mp/subscribe-youtube|The shop location that in 1990 hosted the first McDonaldâ€™s restaurant in Russia reopened June 12, 2022, with a new name and logo after a Russian owner bought all 850 of the US fast-food giantâ€™s franchises in the country. McDonaldâ€™s suspended operations in March in the wake of Moscowâ€™s invasion of Ukraine, then announced on May 16 that it would leave Russia altogether. Three days later, Russian businessman Alexander Govor bought the operation and said he would continue to employ former McDonaldâ€™s employees as he made plans to rebrand and reopen 200 of the outlets by the end of June and the others by the end of the summer.|Support us:|https://subscribe.scmp.com|Follow us on:|Website:  https://www.scmp.com|Facebook:  https://facebook.com/scmp|Twitter:  https://twitter.com/scmpnews|Instagram:  https://instagram.com/scmpnews|Linkedin:  https://www.linkedin.com/company/south-china-morning-post/|#scmp #World #Russia

title: Rory McIlroy's 8-under 62 and 21st victory | Round 4 | RBC Canadian | 2022
description: In the final round of the 2022 RBC Canadian Open, Rory McIlroy shot an 8-under 62 to get to 19-under par and win his 21st PGA TOUR title by two shots.|SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh||||Rory McIlroy will look to defend his title this weekend, as the PGA TOUR returns to St Georgeâ€™s Golf and Country Club for the RBC Canadian Open. The course last hosted the tournament in 2010 when Carl Pettersson was victorious. Three years ago, Northern Irishman McIlroy beat the course record to claim victory finishing seven shots clear of second place. World No. 1 Scottie Scheffler will be looking for a fifth victory this year, having narrowly missed out on another first place finish last weekend in a tense playoff with Sam Burns at the Charles Schwab Challenge. Other notable players teeing up include 2022 PGA Championship winner Justin Thomas, THE PLAYERS Championship winner Cameron Smith as well as Tony Finau, Justin Rose and Tyrell Hatton.||||Check out https://www.pgatour.com for complete coverage along with all the latest news, scoring, and stats!||||Follow PGA TOUR online:||Instagram: https://instagram.com/pgatour/  ||Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PGATour  ||Twitter: https://twitter.com/PGATOUR||TikTok: https://tiktok.com/@pgatour||SoundCloud: https://soundcloud.com/pgatour||||Sign up for exclusive coverage - http://www.pgatourlive.com||PGA TOUR Superstore - http://www.pgatoursuperstore.com/

title: Racism for Sale - BBC Africa Eye documentary
description: In February 2020, a shocking video began to circulate on Chinese social media. A group of African children are being instructed, by a voice off-camera, to chant phrases in Chinese. The kids repeat the words with smiles and enthusiasm â€” but they donâ€™t understand that what theyâ€™re being told to say is â€œI am a black monster and my IQ is low.â€ The clip ignited outrage in China and beyond. |But no-one ever answered the crucial questions: Why was this filmed? This drama tells the story of beauty vlogger Su Yanxi (played by Lin Xinyi) who is threatened by her twin sister He Jinxi (played by Lin Xinyi) and forced to replace her sister to become "contract lovers" with the wealthy president Gu Xicheng (played by Luo Zheng). Gu Xicheng, who wanted to make his sick grandma happy pretended to be in a relationship, yet he found himself slowly becoming more attracted by this optimistic and bright Su Yanxi. description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Sejak malam tadi sampai pagi ini, ratusan warga silih beganti untuk melakukan takziah di Rumah Dinas Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil di Gedung Pakuan, Kota Bandung.||||Warga antusias terus berdatangan untuk menyampaikan duka cita atas meninggalnya Emmeril Eril Khan Mumtadz, putra sulung dari Ridwan Kamil.||||Bahkan, tak sedikit warga dari luar Bandung yang datang untuk melakukan takziah dan menyampain duka cita atas kepergian Eril.||||Secara terbuka, Ridwan Kamil memperbolehkan warga untuk datang masuk ke Gedung Pakuan dan tampak penjagaan memang yang tidak terlalu ketat.||||Karangan bunga juga terlihat memadati halaman serta sekeliling Gedung Pakuan.||||Baca Juga 5 Fakta Desa Cimaung, Lokasi Pemakaman Eril yang Menyuguhkan Wisata Alam Menyejukkan di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298360/5-fakta-desa-cimaung-lokasi-pemakaman-eril-yang-menyuguhkan-wisata-alam-menyejukkan||||Sebelumnya, Jenazah Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril, putra sulung Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil tiba di Gedung Pakuan, Bandung, Jawa Barat, Minggu (12/6/2022) malam.||||Sekitar pukul 20.00 WIB dengan dikawal Petugas Ditlantas Polda Jawa Barat, keluarga dan kerabat serta warga tampak ikut menyambut kedatangan jenazah Eril di Gedung Pakuan.||||Jenazah Eril akan disemayamkan di Gedung Pakuan Bandung dan akan dimakamkan di Pemakaman Cimaung, Kabupaten Bandung pada hari ini, Senin (13/6/2022) pagi.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298363/suasana-pagi-ini-di-gedung-pakuan-warga-terus-berdatangan-untuk-takziah

title: Ganjar Ungkap Sesuatu Ekspresi dari Ridwan Kamil Saat Bertakziah Jenazah Eril
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV  Gubernur Jawa Tengah, Ganjar Pranowo mengatakan ada sesuatu yang terlihat di wajah Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil.||||Saat Ganjar Pranowo bertakziah untuk jenazah Eril pada Minggu, 12 Juni 2022 malam.||||Ganjar Pranowo sempat menceritakan hasil perbincangannya saat bertemu Ridwan Kamil.||||Ganjar Pranowo mengamati, ada raut wajah bahagia dan kesedihan mendalam di saat bersamaan.||||"Tadi saya berbincang banyak dengan Kang Emil, ada sesuatu yang terlihat di wajahnya sebuah kesedihan sekaligus keikhlasan. Tadi beliau sampaikan, ada saatnya saya berbahagia karena dua minggu suasana batin diaduk karena tidak ada kepastian apakah ananda tersayang bisa ditemukan," tutur Ganjar.||||Baca Juga Terkini! Situasi Jelang Pemakaman Eril di Cimaung, Ratusan Personel Dikerahkan! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298358/terkini-situasi-jelang-pemakaman-eril-di-cimaung-ratusan-personel-dikerahkan||||"Meskipun beliau menyatakan berbahagia tapi saya lihat raut mukanya memperlihatkan kesedihan yang sangat menusuk," jelasnya.||||"Tadi cerita beliau utuhnya jasad, wanginya aromanya, menengok ke kanan dengan wajah yang segar, Insya Allah itu menunjukkan proses kebaikan selama di dunia beliau banyak membantu orang," kata Ganjar Pranowo di Gedung Pakuan pada 12 Juni 2022.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Krisna Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298362/ganjar-ungkap-sesuatu-ekspresi-dari-ridwan-kamil-saat-bertakziah-jenazah-eril

title: On Camera: Subway Surfersâ€™ stunt over USâ€™ Williamsburg bridge goes viral; netizens react
description: A group of people were seen running on top of a moving train as it entered U.Sâ€™ Williamsburg. As per videos online, at least eight people were seen on top of the Brooklyn bound train. They were seen skipping and sprinting; some sat and crouched on the roof of the train. Several videos of the group on top of the train went viral on social media. The New York Police Department (NYPD) has said that it was aware of the footage, as per New York Post. It added that the suspects could be charged with trespassing and reckless endangerment. title: Highlights | Round 4 | RBC Canadian | 2022
description: Check out the best shots of the day from Round 4 at the 2022 RBC Canadian Open, featuring Rory McIlroy, Justin Rose, Justin Thomas and Tony Finau among others.|SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh||||Rory McIlroy will look to defend his title this weekend, as the PGA TOUR returns to St Georgeâ€™s Golf and Country Club for the RBC Canadian Open. The course last hosted the tournament in 2010 when Carl Pettersson was victorious. Three years ago, Northern Irishman McIlroy beat the course record to claim victory finishing seven shots clear of second place. World No. 1 Scottie Scheffler will be looking for a fifth victory this year, having narrowly missed out on another first place finish last weekend in a tense playoff with Sam Burns at the Charles Schwab Challenge. Other notable players teeing up include 2022 PGA Championship winner Justin Thomas, THE PLAYERS Championship winner Cameron Smith as well as Tony Finau, Justin Rose and Tyrell Hatton.||||Check out https://www.pgatour.com for complete coverage along with all the latest news, scoring, and stats!||||Follow PGA TOUR online:||Instagram: https://instagram.com/pgatour/  ||Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PGATour  ||Twitter: https://twitter.com/PGATOUR||TikTok: https://tiktok.com/@pgatour||SoundCloud: https://soundcloud.com/pgatour||||Sign up for exclusive coverage - http://www.pgatourlive.com||PGA TOUR Superstore - http://www.pgatoursuperstore.com/

title: Vlog Kondisi Terkini Makam Eril di Cimaung, Kabupaten Bandung
description: Jenazah Eril, Putra Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil akan dimakamkan hari ini. Jenazah akan diberangkatkan dari gedung pakuan Kota Bandung pukul 9.00 WIB menuju pemakaman keluarga di Kecamatan Cimaung, Kabupaten Bandung. Eril akan dimakamkan di makam keluarga yang berada di samping Masjid Al Mumtadz. Warga yang hendak berziarah, bisa dilaksanakan setelah proses pemakaman selesai.|Produser Lapangan, Zaiul Khaq melaporkannya untuk Anda.

title: Wild video shows cat fights off coyote, narrowly escapes attack on Texas porch
description: An encounter between a cat and a coyote was caught on video, with the feline narrowly escaping, as a Texas town deals with a rise in coyote sightings.|Tony Gray's home surveillance camera recorded video of the coyote-cat melee as it unfolded on the Surfside Beach porch early Thursday morning.|"Coyote upstairs on my beach house rear deck..." he wrote on Facebook.|The cat tried frantically to hide or escape from the coyote. It appeared to have suffered a few close calls in the jaws in the wild animal.|Eventually, the feline made its way to safety up the porch support and the coyote moved on.|#caughtonvideo #coyote #cat |READ MORE: An encounter between a cat and a coyote was caught on video, with the feline narrowly escaping, as a Texas town deals with a rise in coyote sightings.|RELATED: 'Lost puppy' taken home by family turns out to be baby coyote|Tony Gray's home surveillance camera recorded video of the coyote-cat melee as it unfolded on the Surfside Beach porch early Thursday morning.|"Coyote upstairs on my beach house rear deck..." he wrote on Facebook.|The cat tried frantically to hide or escape from the coyote. It appeared to have suffered a few close calls in the jaws in the wild animal.|Eventually, the feline made its way to safety up the porch support and the coyote moved on.

title: Senators Strike Bipartisan Gun Deal
description: A bipartisan group of senators announced Sunday there was a tentative agreement of legislation on new gun restrictions. Assault weapons were not banned, but the new bill will allow states to use red flag laws to deny guns to dangerous people and will close the boyfriend loopholes to keep guns from domestic abusers. The deal targets 18 to 21-year-old gun buyers requiring them to wait for enhanced background checks, including a check with local police. Tomorrow, senators and their staff will start fine-tuning the framework hoping to cast the final vote before the August recess. title: Skyrocketing home prices and rents create housing crisis
description: In today's highly competitive housing market, millions of Americans are priced out of buying a home, often competing with all-cash offers well above asking prices. Rents are skyrocketing, too, causing overall housing affordability to collapse at its fastest rate on record. title: Defiant Russia replaces McDonald's with â€œTastyâ€ burger chain - BBC News
description: Russia is determined to show it can defy international sanctions over the war in Ukraine.  |Fast food giant McDonald's pulled out of Russia in protest at the Ukraine invasion and sold off its restaurants - more than 800 of them - to a Russian businessman, Alexander Govor.|Now the first rebranded alternative outlets have reopened in Moscow.  There's a new name: "Vkusno i Tochka" which translates as "Tasty and That's It".|Gone are the Golden Arches, replaced by a stylised letter M, made out of two French fries and a circle for a burger.|But the new owners hope customers won't notice too many differences. They held a press conference in the flagship restaurant on Pushkin Square, where the very first Moscow McDonald's opened 32 years ago.|"Our goal is that our guests do not notice a difference either in quality or ambience," said Oleg Paroyev, CEO of Vkusno i Tochka.|Reeta Chakrabarti presents BBC News at Ten reporting from Moscow by Steve Rosenberg.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#BBCNews

title: Men's Boulder final || Brixen 2022
description: Following back-to-back World Cups last month in Salt Lake City, Utah, USA, the International Federation of Sport Climbing (IFSC) World Cup Series 2022 continues this weekend with the fifth instalment of the season. Returning to Europe, the Italian town of Brixen is set to play host to the next IFSC Boulder World Cup events, from 10 to 12 June 2022. |The IFSC Boulder World Cup Brixen 2022 is the first IFSC competition to take place in Italy since the IFSC Youth World Championships Arco 2019, as well as the first IFSC World Cup to be held in the country since 2018. Moreover, this is the first time that Brixen has hosted an IFSC World Cup, having previously welcomed only continental Sport Climbing competitions including the IFSC Europe Cup this May.|More news: https://bit.ly/3ivwb9v|Subscribe: https://bit.ly/3oveCdv

title: How these mates survived 46 days lost at sea in a tiny boat | 60 Minutes Australia
description: Subscribe here: http://9Soci.al/chmP50wA97J Full Episodes: https://9now.app.link/uNP4qBkmN6 | Lost (2005)|Their story of survival on the high seas is so incredible not even Spielberg could improve on the drama. 46 days lost in a tiny boat, a tinnie, at the mercy of sharks and raging seas. A young Australian butcher and his two mates on holiday in the far flung nation of Kiribati; their tinnie cast into the middle of the Pacific Ocean in a storm. To survive, they caught birds and sharks with their bare hands. Incredibly, six ships sailed past, ignoring their cries for help. In their seventh week lost, a freak wave left them close to death. title: Let's Settle This! Are Cordless Power Tools REALLY Better? Torque, Cutting Speed, Noise, Vibration

title: Redfall - Official Gameplay Reveal - Xbox & Bethesda Games Showcase 2022
description: Redfall is an open-world, co-op FPS from Arkane Austin, the award-winning team behind Prey and Dishonored. Continuing Arkaneâ€™s legacy of carefully crafted worlds and immersive sims, Redfall brings the studioâ€™s signature gameplay to this story-driven action shooter.|Redfall used to look like it was straight out of a postcard.|That was before a legion of vampires staked their claim over the islandâ€¦and its inhabitants. By blocking out the sun and pushing the ocean back from Redfallâ€™s shores, these new vampire overlords have completely cut the island off from the outside world and any hope of rescue. |Thatâ€™s where you come in. Youâ€™ll pick from a roster of four diverse heroes and either go solo or team up with up to three other players to round out your squad. Armed with a wide array of customizable gear, specialized weaponry and unique character abilities, ranging from the scientific to the mystical, youâ€™ll take on the bloodthirsty threat and take back Redfall.|Bite Back when Redfall launches in 2023!|Official Site: Redfall.com|Twitter: twitter.com/playRedfall|Facebook: facebook.com/playRedfall|Instagram: instagram.com/playRedfall|ESRB RATING PENDING: May contain content inappropriate for children. title: Noise makes you sick - How can we deal with noise pollution? | DW Documentary
description: Whether itâ€™s loud trucks, planes taking off or rattling freight trains: Noise makes people sick. But there are innovative solutions to reduce noise. This documentary presents some of them.|So-called "crossbars" are a great relief for many residents of noisy cities. These are new buildings that close gaps between rows of houses to keep street noise out.  |In the Middle Rhine Valley, as many as 600 trains thunder over the tracks in a given day. In recent years, so-called whisper brakes have been installed on many rail cars to reduce rail noise. But for local residents, itâ€™s not enough. They are calling for further "quietâ€ measures.  |The start-up "recalm" wants to use "antisound" to reduce noise in mining vehicles. Until now, drivers had the roar and hum of the machines in their ears for eight hours a day, all but guaranteeing hearing loss. With the new high-tech system, low frequencies are reduced, leading to 50% less noise.  |Owls are silent. Thatâ€™s why they are the perfect model for Professor Jan Werner Delfs of the German Aerospace Center (DLR) in Braunschweig. Along with a colleague, the acoustics expert and aerodynamics engineer is researching the art of silent flight - and thus the possibility of making aircraft fly more quietly.  |#documentary #dwdocumentary |______|DW Documentary gives you knowledge beyond the headlines. title: BREAKING NEWS - Jenazah Eril Anak Ridwan Kamil Disemayamkan di Gedung Pakuan Bandung
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Kurang lebih pukul 19.25 WIB, jenazah Eril tiba di Gedung Pakuan, Bandung.|Terpantau oleh jurnalis Kompas TV di lapangan, pengamanan diperketat menjelang prosesi salat jenazah yang sebelumnya direncanakan akan berlangsung pukul 22.00 WIB.|Ya, setibanya di Gedung Pakuan, Bandung, Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil akan memimpin salat jenazah Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz.|Setelah salat jenazah bersama keluarga selesai, masyarakat diperbolehkan takziah mulai pukul 11 malam hingga pukul 8 pagi hari Senin (13/6).|Setelah itu, pukul 9 pagi, jenazah eril diberangkatkan ke pemakaman di Cimaung, Bandung, Jawa Barat.|Jelang kepulangan Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil dan jenazah Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz ke Bandung, seluruh persiapan dimatangkan; termasuk arus lalu lintas di kawasan kota Bandung.|Polrestabes Bandung mengantisipasi kepadatan yang mungkin bisa terjadi, saat kedatangan Ridwan Kamil dan jenazah Eril.|Satlantas Polrestabes Bandung akan mengawal iring iringan jenazah, mulai dari Gerbang Tol Pasteur hingga ke Gedung Pakuan.|Di rumah duka, pengajian sedang berlangsung untuk Almarhum Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz.|Saat ini, keluarga Ridwan Kamil masih dalam perjalanan menuju Gedung Pakuan.|===|Sahabat Kompas TV, jangan lupa like, comment, dan subscribe channel YouTube Kompas TV, juga aktifkan lonceng notifikasi agar tidak ketinggalan update mengenai isu-isu terkini di Indonesia.|Jangan lewatkan live streaming Kompas TV 24 jam non stop di https://www.kompas.tv/live. title: As bulldozers raze Afreen Fatima's house in Prayagraj, Tharoor, Owaisi question Yogi Govt
description: Support pours in for activist Afreen Faitma after Prayagraj Authorities razed her house. Video of Afreen who is the daughter of Welfare party leader and alleged mastermind of Prayagraj violence has gone viral. Several opposition leaders including Shashi Tharoor and Asaduddin Owaisi have questioned the Yogi govt on the demolition drive. Many JNU students have also come out in support of Afreen Fatima. title: The New Youngest Self-Made Billionaire In The World Is A 25-Year-Old College Dropout | Forbes
description: When Massachusetts Institute of Technology dropout Alexandr Wang made the Forbes 30 Under 30 Enterprise Technology list in 2018, his startup Scale used artificial intelligence to begin automating tasks like image recognition and audio transcription. Back then, its customers included GM Cruise, Alphabet, Uber, P&G and others|Now Wang, 25, is the youngest self-made billionaire. And while he still partners with buzzy companies, today heâ€™s got $350 million in government defense contracts. This has helped Scale hit a $7.3 billion valuation, and give Wang a $1 billion net worth (as he owns 15% of the company).|Scaleâ€™s technology analyzes satellite images much faster than human analysts to determine how much damage Russian bombs are causing in Ukraine. Itâ€™s useful not just for the military. More than 300 companies, including General Motors and Flexport, use Scale, which Wang started when he was 19, to help them pan gold from rivers of raw informationâ€”millions of shipping documents, say, or raw footage from self-driving cars. â€œEvery industry is sitting on huge amounts of data,â€ Wang says, who appeared on the Forbes Under 30 list in 2018. â€œOur goal is to help them unlock the potential of the data and supercharge their businesses with AI.â€|Read the full story on Forbes: https://www.forbes.com/sites/colehorton/2022/05/25/the-new-youngest-self-made-billionaire-in-the-world-is-a-25-year-old-college-dropout/?sh=180cf292494b&utm_source=newsletter&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=under30&cdlcid=5cc06ab31802c8c524853545|Subscribe to FORBES: https://www.youtube.com/user/Forbes?sub_confirmation=1|Stay Connected|Forbes newsletters: https://newsletters.editorial.forbes.com|Forbes on Facebook: http://fb.com/forbes|Forbes Video on Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/forbes|Forbes Video on Instagram: http://instagram.com/forbes|More From Forbes:  http://forbes.com|Forbes covers the intersection of entrepreneurship, wealth, technology, business and lifestyle with a focus on people and success.

title: China warns Taiwan independence would trigger war - BBC News
description: China has warned the US that any attempt to make Taiwan independent from China will trigger military action by Beijing's forces.|Chinese Defence Minister Wei Fenghe met his US counterpart Lloyd Austin on the sidelines of an Asian security summit in Singapore.|Splitting Taiwan from China would leave the Chinese military with no choice but to "fight at any cost", Mr Wei said.|Mr Austin later called Chinese military activity "provocative, destabilising".|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#China #Taiwan #BBCNews
tags: bbc|bbc news|news

title: Bulldozers Out: Home of Prayagraj violence accused razed day after he was arrested
description: Yogi government's bulldozer action is back. The Prayagraj Development Authority has razed the house of June 10 violence 'mastermind' & Welfare Party leader Javed Mohammad's house hours after giving a demolition notice. The authorities claim that the house was illegally constructed which is why they took the action. This drive comes just a day after Javed was named as the key conspirator in triggering Friday's violence in the city or Prayagraj over suspended BJP spokesperson Nupur Sharma's Prophet remarks. Watch this report to know more.|#Javed|#bulldozer #prayagraj #uppolice #yogiadityanath #fridayviolence #nupursharma #bulldozerbaba #prophet #prophetmuhammad

title: What's Behind America's Baby Formula Shortage?
description: Parents across the U.S. are scrambling to find baby formula. Empty store shelves, higher prices and retailers limiting sales have made already anxious parents even more nervous about their kids' health. Abbott, the nationâ€™s biggest infant formula maker, recalled several products and shut down its Michigan manufacturing plant in February after bacteria was found at the site. Four infants who consumed formula produced at the facility got sick with an infection. Two of those infants died. So what led to the baby formula crisis in the U.S. in the first place and how can the nation avoid this happening again?|00:00 - Intro|01:45 - Ch 1. Finding formula|04:27 - Ch 2. title: Momen Jenazah Eril Tiba Di Bandara Soetta
description: Minggu (12/6), tepatnya pukul 15.25 WIB, jenazah Emmeril Khan Mumtafz atau Eril, telah tiba di Tanah Air. Kedatangan tersebut tiba lebih awal dari waktu yang telah diperkirakan sebelumnya.

title: Berkat Amal Kebaikan Eril, Keluarga Ridwan Kamil Diundang Ibadah Haji oleh Pemerintah Arab Saudi
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Di tengah duka, keluarga Ridwan Kamil mengucap syukur atas amal jariah mendiang Emmeril Eril Kahn Mumtaz.||||Berkat amal sang putra, keluarga Ridwan Kamil mendapat undangan khusus untuk menunaikan ibadah haji dari pemerintah Arab Saudi.||||Lewat unggahan video di media sosial, kutipan pernyataan Ibunda Eril, Atalia Praratya, disampaikan dalam pengajian di Rumah Dinas Gubernur Jabar.||||Atalia meyakini, undangan naik haji dari pemerintah Arab Saudi karena kebaikan putranya selama ini.||||Ucap syukur tak henti disampaikan Atalia.||||Jelang kepulangan Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil dan jenazah Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz ke Bandung, seluruh persiapan dimatangkan; termasuk arus lalu lintas di kawasan kota Bandung.||||Polrestabes Bandung mengantisipasi kepadatan yang mungkin bisa terjadi, saat kedatangan Ridwan Kamil dan jenazah Eril.||||Satlantas Polrestabes Bandung akan mengawal iring iringan jenazah, mulai dari Gerbang Tol Pasteur hingga ke Gedung Pakuan.||||Di rumah duka, pengajian sedang berlangsung untuk Almarhum Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz.||||Saat ini, keluarga Ridwan Kamil masih dalam perjalanan menuju Gedung Pakuan.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298304/berkat-amal-kebaikan-eril-keluarga-ridwan-kamil-diundang-ibadah-haji-oleh-pemerintah-arab-saudi

title: Russian shelling causes huge chemical fire in Ukrainian city of Severodonetsk - BBC News
description: Russian shelling has caused a huge fire at a chemical plant in Ukraine's Severodonetsk city where "non-stop" fighting rages, the regional head says.|Serhiy Haidai told Ukrainian TV that Saturday's blaze started after a leak of tens of tonnes of oil from damaged radiators at the Azot plant.|Hundreds of civilians are reportedly sheltering at the plant.|Severodonetsk has become the focal point of Russia's efforts to advance in eastern Ukraine.|Ukrainian officials have also said their army is running out of ammunition as it engages in intense artillery battles with invading Russian forces.|Please subscribe HERE http://bit.ly/1rbfUog|#Russia #Ukraine #BBCNews

title: Biggest Unanswered Questions In Jurassic World Dominion
description: As the third film in the new "Jurassic World" trilogy, "Jurassic World: Dominion" had a lot of ground to cover. It needed to bring a satisfying conclusion to the new characters introduced to the world while also setting the table for future adventures if the franchise continues. The filmmakers went above and beyond by actually reuniting the beloved trio of Sam Neil, Laura Dern, and Jeff Goldblum, from the first "Jurassic Park." With such a packed cast and so much globetrotting dinosaur action, it makes that not every plot point was wrapped up neatly with a bow by the time the credits rolled. Here are the biggest unanswered questions in "Jurassic World: Dominion."|#jurassicworld #jurassicworlddominion #dinosaurs |How does the dinosaur preserve work? | 0:00|What else can Maisie's DNA do? | 1:14|What else was Dodgson planning? | 2:22|What happens to Dr. Wu? | 3:39|What about other dinosaur breeders? | 4:52|Will dinosaurs still be used as weapons? | 5:36|What happens to Claire and Owen? | 6:49|What happens to Alan and Ellie? | 7:59|Has Ian's outlook changed? | 9:05|What does Maisie do next? | 10:17|How did Dodgson get the Barbasol? | 11:12|Read Full Article:  https://www.looper.com/890430/biggest-unanswered-questions-in-jurassic-world-dominion/
tags: looper|jurassic world dominion|dinosaurs|questions|dinosaur preserve

title: The Power To See Someone's Past & Future | Crime Patrol | Inspector Series
description: Click here to Subscribe to SET India: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1|Click here to watch more episodes of the Inspector Series:|https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLzufeTFnhupwPXaxlzdWOhhlyKczeyYvR|Crime series that will give you literal spine chills and cases turning out to be unbelievably true. From attacking innocents to bludgeoning them. Every case will ignite a fire, will put one in agony, and hunger for justice will prevail. |An eminent astrologer and his family are eliminated overnight in their house in Kasturi Nagar, Madhya Pradesh. Police find them buried outside the house but are still clueless about the criminal. As the case unfolds, we find how the astrologer had a myth where an object in a red cloth gave him superpowers to see anyone's past and future. Did superstition and fraud lead to this crime? Stay tuned!|Show Name: Crime Patrol|Host: Anup Soni|Producers: Prem Krishen Malhotra, Sunil Mehta, Vipul D. Shah, Anirban Bhattacharyya|#crimepatrol #à¤•à¥à¤°à¤¾à¤‡à¤®à¤ªà¥‡à¤Ÿà¥à¤°à¥‹à¤² #SETIndia|About Crime Patrol :|-----------------------------------|Crimes that tell us, we need to be careful, we need to be watchful. Crimes that tell us lives could have been saved. Every crime we hear of, either warns us to be careful or scares us, it could happen to us. Every crime ignites a feeling, 'It should not have happened. Would knowing the 'Why' behind a crime, help in stopping a crime from happening?' I donâ€™t like the way he looks at me', 'I donâ€™t like the way he/she is behaving', 'I think he/she is out of his/her mind', 'I think he/she has gone crazy'. That gaze, that quirky smile, that persistent stare which unnerves. It is difficult to understand the intentions but the hints are there. In a house a husband and wife argue, fight. A vessel comes flying, a glass breaks. The husband is angry and the wife is upset. That hatred, that ego. The distance keeps growing. It is difficult to comprehend the damage, but the cracks are there. Feelingsâ€¦ expressions. Misunderstood, unresolved callings of the heart. The cracks are there. Too wide to be missed. Yet when the heart takes over the mind, the outcome is a mindless tragedy. Crime Patrol - Satark Rahe will attempt to look at the signs, the signals that are always there before these mindless crimes are committed. Instincts/Feelings/Signals that so often tell us that not everything is normal. Maybe, that signal/feeling/instinct is just not enough to believe it could result in a crime. Unfortunately, after the crime is committed, those same signals come haunting.|The Power To See Someone's Past & Future | Crime Patrol | Inspector Series

title: Pak's fake news factory over Prophet row exposed; Report details hashtags, deceptive pics
description: Pak using social media to defame India after row over remarks on Prophet by suspended BJP leader. Several Pak media houses ran wrong news that Oman's grand mufti announced a boycott of Indian goods. Ex-envoy Abdul Basit wrongfully said expelled BJP leader Naveen Jindal is industrialist Sajjan Jindal's brother. title: SMART PAINTING HACKS FOR BEGINNERS
description: Hello, crafty people! ||Here is a new collection of incredible ideas and creative hacks to help you to become a better artist. We will show you several simple drawing exercises that will help you to improve your drawing skills. You will learn different techniques for creating unusual gradients, which will allow you to draw the most unusual flowers like a hibiscus or a stunning bird. You will repeat all of them without any problem. You will see how to use rope to create a real masterpiece. Sounds great, right? title: Prosesi Penerimaan Jenazah Eril di Gedung Pakuan Bandung, Keluarga & Kerabat Jadi Saksi
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Jenazah Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz baru saja sampai di Gedung Pakuan, Minggu (12/6).||||Keluarga, kerabat, dan warga yang berada di Gedung Pakuan, Bandung, menjadi saksi penerimaan jenazah yang baru saja dibawa dari Bandara Soekarno-Hatta.||||Sebelumnya, kurang lebih pukul 19.25 WIB, rombongan pengantar jenazah Eril tiba di Gedung Pakuan, Bandung.||||Terpantau oleh jurnalis Kompas TV di lapangan, pengamanan diperketat menjelang prosesi salat jenazah yang sebelumnya direncanakan akan berlangsung pukul 22.00 WIB.||||Ya, setibanya di Gedung Pakuan, Bandung, Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil akan memimpin salat jenazah Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz.||||Setelah salat jenazah bersama keluarga selesai, masyarakat diperbolehkan takziah mulai pukul 11 malam hingga pukul 8 pagi hari Senin (13/6).||||Setelah itu, pukul 9 pagi, jenazah Eril diberangkatkan ke pemakaman di Cimaung, Bandung, Jawa Barat.||||Jelang rangkaian pemakaman jenazah Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz ke Bandung, seluruh persiapan dimatangkan; termasuk arus lalu lintas di kawasan kota Bandung.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298317/prosesi-penerimaan-jenazah-eril-di-gedung-pakuan-bandung-keluarga-kerabat-jadi-saksi

title: Cheese and Ham Filled Italian Flat Bread from Scratch
description: A piadina is a type of Italian flat bread that can be filled with many different exciting fillings. You can make it from scratch, or alternatively, buy readymade flat bread.  Either way I guarantee a delicious meal that even the kids will enjoy. Piadina is also a fun Italian street food in which youâ€™ll find many combinations of fillings.|The flat bread dough comes together by simply mixing flour, water, olive oil, baking powder and salt.  You can make it by hand as I did, or use a mixer to knead the dough.  I suggest making extra dough, as you can freeze it ready to cook anytime for fresh bread.  For the filling, I have kept it simple.  Cheese, rocket lettuce and prosciutto.  You can use Mozzarella cheese or (My preference) squacquerone if you can find it.|ğŸ‘‰ Get this written recipe link here:  https://recipe30.com/italian-flat-bread.html/|â–¶ Check out my favourite kitchen tools here (affiliate):  https://www.amazon.com/shop/recipe30  |â–¶ Follow me on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/recipe30/|â–¶ Follow me on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/recipe30/|â–¶Music by Epidemic Sound:  https://www.epidemicsound.com/referral/39ip8k|Want to mail me something? |Fan mail and products|MAILING ADDRESS:|RECIPE30|PO BOX 416|MOUNT MARTHA 3934|VICTORIA AUSTRALIA

title: China warns US over support for Taiwan's independence | DW News

title: Ganjar Pranowo, Khofifah Indar Parawansa, & Sejumlah Pejabat Publik Hadir di Salat Jenazah Eril
description: BANDUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Presiden Joko Widodo mengucapkan belasungkawa kepada Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil, atas wafatnya putra pertamanya, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz.||||Presiden menitip doa agar keluarga Ridwan Kamil tabah dan sabar.||||Warga berkesempatan untuk salat jenazah dan melayat Almarhum Eril di Gedung Pakuan.||||MUI mengingatkan beberapa hal yang perlu diperhatikan.||||Berikut perbincangan dengan Sekretaris Umum MUI Kota Bandung, Asep Ahmad Faturohman dalam program sebelumnya.||||Jenazah Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz akan dimakamkan di pemakaman keluarga di wilayah Cimaung, Kabupaten Bandung.||||Menurut rencana, keberangkatan jenazah Eril dari Gedung Pakuan menuju pemakaman keluarga di Cimaung dijadwalkan pada jam 9 pagi.||||Nantinya, warga diperbolehkan berziarah ke makam Eril usai prosesi pemamakan oleh pihak keluarga selesai.||||_____||||Jangan lewatkan live streaming Kompas TV 24 jam nonstop di https://www.kompas.tv/live.||||Agar tidak ketinggalan berita-berita terkini, terlengkap, serta laporan langsung dari berbagai daerah di Indonesia. title: Diproses Serah Terima, Ini Detik-detik Momen Jenazah Eril Masuk ke Cargo Bandara Soekarno-Hatta
description: TANGERANG, KOMPAS.TV - Kasatlantas Bandara Soekarno-Hatta, kompol Bambang Askar Sodiq, mengatakan rekayasa lalu lintas akan diterapkan sepanjang rute Jakarta-Bandung.||||Pengamanan ketat juga akan dilakukan selama prosesi penjemputan jenazah ke landasan oleh personel gabungan, TNI-Polri dan pihak Angkasa Pura.||||Ya, jenazah putra sulung Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz, telah tiba di Indonesia.||||Jenazah tiba di Tanah Air, melalui Bandara Soekarno-Hatta.||||Polantas Bandara Soekarno-Hatta memastikan akan mengawal perjalanan jenazah Eril dari bandara menuju Bandung, Jawa Barat.||||Pulangnya jasad eril ke Tanah Air, jadi jawaban Sang Maha Kuasa, atas doa kedua orang tua, Ridwan Kamil dan Atalia Praratya, beserta keluarga, kerabat, dan khalayak.||||_____||||Jangan lewatkan live streaming Kompas TV 24 jam nonstop di https://www.kompas.tv/live.||||Agar tidak ketinggalan berita-berita terkini, terlengkap, serta laporan langsung dari berbagai daerah di Indonesia. Yuk, subscribe channel YouTube Kompas TV!||||Aktifkan juga lonceng supaya kamu dapat notifikasi video terbaru dari Kompas TV. Sahabat Kompas TV juga bisa memperoleh informasi terkini melalui website: https://www.kompas.tv.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298260/diproses-serah-terima-ini-detik-detik-momen-jenazah-eril-masuk-ke-cargo-bandara-soekarno-hatta

title: Detik-detik Jenazah Eril Tiba di Bandara Soekarno-Hatta
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Putra sulung Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil, Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz alias Eril tiba di Bandara Soekarno-Hatta, Banten, Indonesia pada Minggu (12/6) pukul 15.30 WIB.||||Perjalanan jenazah anak Ridwan Kamil ini menempuh sekitar 17 jam setelah terbang dari Swiss hingga Indonesia.||||Selanjutnya, setelah melakukan proses serah terima jenazah di Terminal Kargo Jenazah Bandara Soekarno-Hatta, jenazah Eril akan langsung bertolak ke Bandung.||||Baca Juga Jenazah Eril Diberangkatkan ke Bandung untuk Disemayamkan di Gedung Pakuan di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298274/jenazah-eril-diberangkatkan-ke-bandung-untuk-disemayamkan-di-gedung-pakuan||||Nantinya, jenazah Eril akan disemayamkan di Gedung Pakuan Bandung.||||Sebelumnya, pihak keluarga Ridwan Kamil menyebutkan bahwa masyarakat yang ingin turut mendoakan atau bertakziah ke Gedung Pakuan dipersilakan pada pukul 10 malam hingga 8 pagi.||||Lalu, jenazah Eril akan dimakamkan keesokan harinya, Senin (13/6) pagi di DEsa Cimaung, Kabupaten Bandung.||||Video Editor: Agung Ramdani||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298285/detik-detik-jenazah-eril-tiba-di-bandara-soekarno-hatta

title: Ukraine troops hold out in Sievierodonetsk ++ Scholz to visit Kyiv | Ukraine Update
description: Ukraine says it remains in control of a crucial chemical plant in the eastern city of Sievierodonetsk, where hundreds of civilians are sheltering.|The Luhansk regional governor rejected claims by pro-Russian separatists that Ukrainian troops had been blockaded there. He says Ukrainian forces continue to hold an industrial zone in the city. The area has seen consistent, bitter street battles and heavy Russian shelling. Sievierodonetsk has become the epicenter of the battle in eastern Ukraine.|German Chancellor Olaf Scholz will travel to Ukraine's capital Kyiv before the end of June, according to media sources. |The "Bild" newspaper reports that the chancellor will visit with French President Emmanuel Macron and Italian Prime Minister Mario Draghi. This will mark the first time Scholz has visited the Ukrainian capital since the war began. The German government has so far declined to comment on the report.|"Delicious, Full Stop". That's the name given to the new fast food chain replacing former McDonald's restaurants in Russia. The new name was revealed ahead of their reopening on Sunday. The change comes after McDonald's closed its 850 Russian outlets in response to Moscow's invasion of Ukraine.|Russian forces occupying southern Ukraine have begun handing out passports. 23 locals - including the new Moscow-installed governor of Kherson - have accepted Russian citizenship. title: 'Return gift...': BJP MLA triggers row with video of UP cops beating 'rioters'
description: BJP MLA Shalabh Mani Tripathi shares  a video of alleged rioters being brutally thrashed by the Uttar Pradesh police. The MLA captioned the video as 'return gift to rioters'. In the video around nine men can be seen begging and trying to block the blows being rained on them incessantly by two policemen. The place appears to be a police station but the location is not clear yet. This video which has now gone viral caught the attention of former U.P CM Akhilesh Yadav. Akhilesh slammed the 'police brutality' and questioned the Yogi govt over the same. Watch this report to know more.|#uppolice #uprioters #yogiadityanath #dangawadi #violenceviolencedialogue #uppolice #rioters

title: Alien territory - NASA joins hunt for UFOs, Unidentified Aerial Phenomena gain mainstream traction
description: NASA is launching a study of UFOs as part of a new push toward high-risk, high-impact science. UFO study, once a poorly-regarded research backwater, is gaining more mainstream traction. NASA sees this a step in trying to explain mysterious sightings known as unidentified aerial phenomena (UAPs). A U.S. Intel report last year cataloged 144 sightings that couldn't be explained - it did not rule out alien origin.|#UFO #Alien UAP #Space #UFOs #UFOSightings #UAPs #UAP #Trends #Trending #Viral #BreakingNews #Watch #Video #Breaking #UnidentifiedFlyingObject #UnidentifiedAerialPhenomena #India #Bharat #NASA #USA

title: Putin Moves Tor & Pantsir In For Snake Island | Can Russian Missile Systems Repel Ukraine's HIMARS?
description: Russia has reportedly reinforced its seized outpost on Snake Island with additional surface-to-air missile (SAM) systems. Experts say multiple Tor and Pantsir short-range air defence systems are now involved in the defence of the small island. Experts say the arrival of M30/31 guided rockets and HIMARS launchers in Ukraine could pose problems for the Russian military. title: Keluarga RK Minta Warga & Pers Jaga Privasi Wanita Asal Swiss yang Temukan Eril, Geraldine Beldi
description: TANGERANG, KOMPAS.TV - Elpi Nazmuzzaman, mewakili keluarga Ridwan Kamil, berterima kasih kepada seluruh pihak yang telah membantu proses pencarian Eril.||||Dari warga yang terus mendoakan, pemerintah Indonesia dan Swiss, hingga beberapa sosok warga asal kota Bern yang menemukan Eril.||||Tak lupa juga, Elpi meminta kepada warga dan awak media untuk menjaga privasi dari Geraldine Beldi, guru sekolah dasar asal Swiss yang sebelumnya menemukan Eril di Bendungan Engehalde.||||Sebelumnya, Ridwan Kamil menemui Geraldine Beldi, guru sekolah dasar yang menemukan Eril di Pintu Air Engehalde, Swiss.||||Geraldine menemukan Eril saat berjalan pagi menuju tempatnya mengajar, dan langsung menelepon polisi Swiss, sehingga Eril bisa dievakuasi.||||Ridwan Kamil berterima kasih secara langsung kepada Geraldine, sebelum berangkat pulang ke Indonesia.||||Bukan hanya Sungai Aare yang terhubung mendalam dengan keluarga Ridwan Kamil.||||Ada juga dua warga Swiss yang punya tempat khusus di hati keluarga.||||Yang pertama, Geraldine Beldi namanya; seorang guru yang menemukan Eril di Pintu Air Engehalde setelah dua pekan pencarian.||||Saat bertemu, keduanya sempat berbincang.||||Ada pula Heinrich, warga Bern yang saat kejadian, membantu adik perempuan Eril, Zara, dan temannya naik ke daratan.||||Sungai Aare dan keluarga Eril akan selalu terhubung dalam menghadapi lembaran hidup, menerima takdir Yang Maha Kuasa.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298277/keluarga-rk-minta-warga-pers-jaga-privasi-wanita-asal-swiss-yang-temukan-eril-geraldine-beldi

title: Hunting for LIONFISH in TOBAGO!! Caribbean SEAFOOD Feast in Pigeon Point, Tobago!!
description: ğŸ‡¹ğŸ‡¹CHEF JASON PERU: https://www.instagram.com/chefjasonperu/ |ğŸ‡¹ğŸ‡¹CANDICE: https://www.instagram.com/candicemohan.tt |ğŸ‡¹ğŸ‡¹DAVID: https://www.instagram.com/foodieruntt  |ğŸ‡¹ğŸ‡¹DAVE: https://www.instagram.com/davelli27 |ğŸŒ MY TRAVEL/FOOD BLOG: https://davidsbeenhere.com/ |My time in Tobago continued with one of the most fun and unique experiences Iâ€™ve ever had while traveling. Come with me as I enjoy Tobago seafood after hunting lionfish in the Caribbean Sea!|My friend Chef Jason Peru and I started our day in Pigeon Point on the Caribbean side of the island. We headed out from Pigeon Point Heritage Park and would head out on a boat and go spearfishing underwater!|âš½ï¸BOL: https://www.instagram.com/bol.football  |ğŸ‘• DAVIDâ€™S BEEN HERE MERCH: https://teespring.com/stores/davids-been-here |Thereâ€™s a stand on the beach where the vendor sells beautiful conch shells of all different sizes. I bought three of them for my daughters and my niece for 120 TTD.|From there, we met up with our friends David and Dave. I couldnâ€™t wait to get out on the boat and get in the water. I hadnâ€™t gone spearfishing since I was a teenager!|They taught me how to load and use the speargun before we hopped on our boat, The Frontier 1. The sun was intense even though it was the morning. Always wear sunscreen!|Then, they served us some pigtail and cow heel soup. The cow heels are gelatinous and super tasty. It also contained large chunks of pumpkin and was almost like a gumbo. I loved it!|After eating, I put on my snorkel mask and hopped into the water and catching a lionfish! We got two lionfish as well as a third fish and then enjoyed some breadfruit chips back on the boat.|Then, we headed over to No Manâ€™s Land, a peninsula thatâ€™s uninhabited. We could see people windsurfing. They also hold jazz music and fashion events there!|No Manâ€™s Land is beautiful. Itâ€™s an empty island with a hut where they were barbecuing some chicken and corn, and also had some sweets including coconut fudge, peanut fudge, nut brittle, preserved red mango, tamarind balls, and more! |We bought some tamarind balls, peanut fudge, and nut brittle. Each cost 10 TTD, or roughly $1.50 USD per item. The peanut fudge was like a dense bar of peanut butter, while the tamarind balls were tart and very sugary!|The drumstick was coated in a sweet barbecue sauce. The meat fell right off the bone! Then, I watched our friend Dave clean and butcher the lionfish. He easily removed the scales using the back of a knife. He had to be careful because of the poisonous spines!|Lionfish are invasive in the waters around Tobago, so itâ€™s allowed and encouraged to hunt them. He filleted one lionfish and left the other whole so we could grill it whole. Weâ€™d eat the filets raw with some lime!|It was just like sashimi! It was fresh but a little tough. I liked it a lot! Then, Jason began slicing a breadfruit and put some garlic and thyme inside the slits before placing it on the fire to roast. |He dipped the fish into the sea to salt it and then placed it on the grill. Then, they cut filets from the squirrel fish weâ€™d caught. Jason and I ate everything on a large leaf!|We left just as more tourists were visiting. Jason, Candice and I had to dive back into the water! Priya is a happy-go-lucky woman in her early 30s, not married so far, and quite sure that she wouldn't be able to get married ever. She takes tuition for college students and is happy with the world. Ram Kapoor, a wealthy man in his early 40s, is a ruthless entrepreneur who also believes that he has missed the bus of marriage. But as fate would have it, they bump into each other through a minor car accident which hurts their egos more than their vehicles and then after a series of miscommunications and misunderstandings, destiny contrives once again to get the two married. title: J&K Security Forces avenge the killing of cop Riyaz Ahmad, 3 Lashkar terrorists killed in encounter
description: Three Lashkar terrorists killed in an overnight encounter with Security Forces in Pulwama, J&K. The encounter broke out Saturday in Drabgam area in South Kashmir & one terrorist was killed before the night fell. The police maintained a tight cordon during the night to stop the terrorists from fleeing. Two more terrorists were killed when the firing resumed early Sunday morning. Kashmir Inspector General of Police stated all three were locals, linked with Lashkar-e-Taiba.|#Kashmir #Terror #Encounter #Terrorists #JammuKashmir #Jammu #Pulwama #SouthKashmir #India #Bharat #Trends #Trending #Viral #Watch #Video #BreakingNews #Police #Cop #Security #SecurityForces #Forces #Laskhar #LashkareTaiba

title: Severodonetsk nightmare: 800 Ukraine troops & civilians trapped in Azot Plant amid Russian shelling
description: Bitter fighting in Severodonetsk - the last major city not in Russian control in the region of Luhansk. Governor stated Ukraine still in control of Azot plant, where 100s are sheltering from incessant Russian shelling. A Russia-backed separatist group claimed 300-400 Ukrainian fighters also trapped at the Azot plant. Ukraine says about 800 people hiding in the Azot factory, including 200 employees, 600 Severodonetsk residents. Kyiv fears Severodonetsk may be the next Mariupol - Ukrainians spent weeks under siege before surrendering.
