title: EKSKLUSIF: Jenazah Eril Telah Tiba di Indonesia Melalui Bandara Soetta
description: KOMPAS.TV - Jenazah Putra Gubernur Jawa Barat Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz telah dipulangkan dari Swiss menuju tanah air dalam pesawat yang sama dengan sang ayah.||||Sore ini, (12/06) jenazah Eril telah di Bandara Soekarno-Hatta. Pihak keluarga akan menjemput jenazah Eril diantaranya adalah Atalia ke area cargo Bandara Soetta untuk bersama-sama menerima penyerahan jenazah Eril dari pihak otoritas Bandara Soetta.||||Baca Juga Karangan Bunga untuk Eril Capai 1.700 di Gedung Pakuan, Dukungan bagi Keluarga Ridwan Kamil di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298236/karangan-bunga-untuk-eril-capai-1-700-di-gedung-pakuan-dukungan-bagi-keluarga-ridwan-kamil||||Kementerian Luar Negeri akan mewakilkan prosesi penyerahan jenazah Eril. Selaian Atalia, adik dari almarhum Eril juga akan ikut menjemput sang kakak.||||Proses penyerah jenzah juga akan percepat hanya akan memakan waktu 30-40 menit.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298255/eksklusif-jenazah-eril-telah-tiba-di-indonesia-melalui-bandara-soetta
tags: bandara soetta|eril|jenazah eril|jenazah eril tiba|kedatangan jenazah eril|ridwan kamil

title: Ridwan Kamil & Atalia Bergegas ke Bandung Bersama Jenazah Eril, Diperkirakan Tiba Pukul 19.00 WIB
description: KOMPAS.TV - Polrestabes Bandung sudah menyiapkan rencana pengamanan jalur yang akan dilalui oleh Gubernur Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil.||||Menurut rencana RK, bersama jenazah sang anak, Almarhum Emmeril Eril Kahn Mumtadz, menuju ke Gedung Pakuan melalui Gerbang Tol Pasteur.||||Untuk pengamanan dan pengawalan senin besok menuju lokasi permakaman pun sudah disiapkan untuk antisipasi kemacetan.||||Polrestabes Bandung mengimbau warga Kota Bandung untuk menggunakan jalur alternatif, jika berkendara di jalur kedatangan jenazah, agar tak terjebak kemacetan.||||Setibanya di Gedung Pakuan, Bandung, Jawa Barat, Ridwan Kamil akan memimpin halat jenazah Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz.||||Setelah shalat jenazah bersama keluarga selesai, masyarakat diperbolehkan takziah mulai pukul 11 malam hingga pukul 8 pagi hari Senin (13/6).||||Kemudian, pukul 9 pagi, jenazah Eril diberangkatkan ke pemakaman di Cimaung, Bandung, Jawa Barat.||||_____                                            ||||Jangan lewatkan live streaming Kompas TV 24 jam nonstop di https://www.kompas.tv/live.||||Agar tidak ketinggalan berita-berita terkini, terlengkap, serta laporan langsung dari berbagai daerah di Indonesia. Yuk, subscribe channel YouTube Kompas TV!||||Aktifkan juga lonceng supaya kamu dapat notifikasi video terbaru dari Kompas TV. Sahabat Kompas TV juga bisa memperoleh informasi terkini melalui website: https://www.kompas.tv.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298297/ridwan-kamil-atalia-bergegas-ke-bandung-bersama-jenazah-eril-diperkirakan-tiba-pukul-19-00-wib

title: Atalia dan Zara Jemput Jenazah Eril di Bandara, Ikut Rombongan Antar Eril ke Bandung
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS TV  Atalia Praratya dan Zara ikut menjemput jenazah Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril di Bandara Soekarno Hatta pada Minggu (12/6) sore.||||Keduanya kemudian akan bersama rombongan keluarga menuju Gedung Pakuan Bandung untuk menyalatkan Eril.||||Ridwan Kamil selaku ayah Eril akan memimpin keluarga besar untuk laksanakan salat jenazah.||||Baca Juga Setibanya di Tanah Air, Ridwan Kamil akan Pimpin Salat Jenazah Eril di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298229/setibanya-di-tanah-air-ridwan-kamil-akan-pimpin-salat-jenazah-eril||||"Ibu Atalia dan adik Eril akan datang menjemput ke sini (Bandara Soekarno Hatta), sehingga nanti akan bersama-sama rombongan, membersamai jenazah menuju Gedung Pakuan," ujar Erwin Muniruzaman, kakak Ridwan Kamil.||||Ridwan Kamil sendiri menjemput jenazah Eril di Bern, Swiss. Lalu ia bersama jenazah Eril terbang ke Indonesia.||||Ridwan Kamil dan jenazah Eril tiba di Indonesia pada Minggu (12/6) sore dengan menggunakan penerbangan.||||Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz atau Eril akan dimakamkan pada Senin (13/6) di di samping Masjid Al-Mumtadz, kawasan Islamic Center Baitul Ridwan.||||Warga diperbolehkan hadir di pemakaman Eril, dengan syarat tertib dan tidak mendokumentasikan untuk kebutuhan pribadi.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298239/atalia-dan-zara-jemput-jenazah-eril-di-bandara-ikut-rombongan-antar-eril-ke-bandung

title: [FULL] Pidato Perpisahan Greysia Polii dari Panggung Bulu Tangkis di Testimonial Day
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS TV  Greysia Polii putuskan gantung raket atau berhenti dari karier bulu tangkisnya tahun ini.||||Acara perpisahan Greysia Polii dengan panggung bulu tangkis digelar di Istora Senayan, Minggu (12/6).||||Dalam acara tersebut, ia sampaikan pidato perpisahan yang mengharukan.||||Baca Juga Greysia Polii Gantung Raket, Pemerintah Jamin Purnaprestasi Atlet sebagai ASN di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298184/greysia-polii-gantung-raket-pemerintah-jamin-purnaprestasi-atlet-sebagai-asn||||Ia dalam kesempatan tersebut menyampaikan apresiasi khusus untuk pasangan ganda putri terakhirnya, Apriyani Rahayu.||||"Dan partner saya yang terakhir, Apriyani Rahayu. You are the best," ucap Greysia di hadapan para hadirin.||||"Terima kasih karena kehadiran dia itu yang membuat saya menginspirasi saya, berlatih kembali. Lima tahun ini adalah lima tahun yang berharga, Pri," lanjutnya.||||Dalam acara tersebut hadir sejumlah atlet dan pengurus olahraga di Indonesia termasuk PBSI.||||Greysia Polii menangis ketika video perjalanan kariernya ditayangkan di Istora, dan membuat ruangan bergemuruh.||||Video menunjukkan perjalanan karier Greysia Polii, yang merupakan ratu ganda putri Indonesia.||||Momen dramatis di Istora juga terjadi ketika sang pasangan ganda putri Apriyani Rahayu memeluk erat Greysia.||||Seperti diketahui, Apriyani merupakan sosok penting dalam perjalanan karier Greysia Polii, terutama beberapa tahun terakhir.||||Greysia Polii putuskan gantung raket atau pensiun dari panggung bulu tangkis tahun ini.||||Sepanjang kariernya, Greysia Polii sumbangkan banyak prestasi untuk bulu tangkis Indonesia.||||Prestasi paling dikenang adalah medali emas bersama Apriyani dalam gelaran Olimpiade Tokyo 2020 yang digelar 2021 lalu.||||Video Editor: Laurensius Galih||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298189/full-pidato-perpisahan-greysia-polii-dari-panggung-bulu-tangkis-di-testimonial-day

title: Jenazah Eril Tiba di Bandara Soetta Sore Hari Ini
description: KOMPAS.TV - Jenazah putra sulung Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil, Emeril Khan Mumtadz dijadwalkan tiba di Indonesia, pada Minggu (12/06) sore ini. Jenazah tiba di tanah air melalui Bandara Soekarno Hatta.||||Polantas Bandara Soekarno Hatta memastikan akan mengawal perjalanan jenazah Eril dari bandara menuju Bandung, Jawa Barat.||||Baca Juga Pesan Atalia untuk Warga yang Hadiri Pemakaman Eril: Tidak Melalukan Dokumentasi Pribadi di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298188/pesan-atalia-untuk-warga-yang-hadiri-pemakaman-eril-tidak-melalukan-dokumentasi-pribadi||||Kasatlantas Bandara Soekarno Hatta Kompol Bambang Askar Sodiq mengatakan, rekayasa lalu lintas akan diterapkan sepanjang rute Jakarta-Bandung.||||Pengamanan ketat juga akan dilakukan selama prosesi penjemputan jenazah ke landasan oleh personel gabungan TNI-Polri dan pihak angkasa pura.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298194/jenazah-eril-tiba-di-bandara-soetta-sore-hari-ini

title: How to choose the RIGHT stud shape (important)
description: Which stud shape is the best on your football boots, and how do you choose between them? In today's video, JayMike talks you through the differences between conical and bladed studs on your football boots to help you decide which stud shape you should go for when you buy new football boots. Here, JayMike will also go over why conical or rounded studs are great for comfort and rotational movements, whereas the bladed studs on speed boots are often more aggressive and better for acceleration and responsive movements - AND, he will also tell you why bladed studs on artificial grass or turf is a bad idea. title: Mumbai: Two men who stop to save bird's life fatally hit by taxi on Bandra-Worli Sea Link
description: A shocking video of two men being hit by a car on Mumbai's Bandra-Worli Sea Link has gone viral. The horrific accident happened when they got down from the car to save an injured bird hit by their car. CCTV footage shows a taxi coming at a high speed hitting them and throwing them away in the air. Both of them died in the accident. Watch this video to know more.|#Mumbai #SeaLink #Accident #Tragedy #BandraWorliSeaLink

title: Mandi di Sungai 3 Pelajar SMK Kota Padang Hanyut Terseret Arus, Pencarian Terkendala Cuaca Buruk!
description: PADANG, KOMPAS.TV - Tiga remaja yang hanyut di lubuk minturun Kota Padang, Sumatera Barat, hingga kini masih dalam pencarian.||||Tim SAR dibantu warga menyisir daerah aliran sungai, untuk mencari ketiga remaja yang hanyut saat sedang mandi di Lubuk Minturun, Kota Padang.||||Tim SAR gabungan masih bersiaga di lokasi.||||Penyisiran di air dilakukan saat cuaca membaik, dan debit air sungai Lubuk Minturun mulai turun.||||Remaja yang hanyut diketahui merupakan pelajar SMK di Kota Padang.||||Baca Juga Polisi Tangkap Pelaku Pembunuhan di Kota Malang, Korban Dihanyutkan ke Sungai di https://www.kompas.tv/article/297019/polisi-tangkap-pelaku-pembunuhan-di-kota-malang-korban-dihanyutkan-ke-sungai||||Mereka diduga tidak mengetahui, bahwa kondisi cuaca saat itu hujan lebat membuat debit air sungai menjadi tinggi.||||Sebelumnya ketiga remaja hanyut, terseret air bah di kawasan Lubuk Minturun, Kota Padang, Sumatera Barat.||||Ketiganya diduga terseret arus bah, saat beraktivitas di sekitar sungai.||||Dari empat remaja yang sedang mandi di sungai, tiga di antaranya hanyut terseret arus.||||Satu lainnya menyelamatkan diri, dan melaporkan peristiwa ini kepada warga.||||Pencarian koban terkendala oleh cuaca buruk, dan arus yang masih deras.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298153/mandi-di-sungai-3-pelajar-smk-kota-padang-hanyut-terseret-arus-pencarian-terkendala-cuaca-buruk

title: Introducing ARK: Fjordur Free DLC!
description: Fjordur is launching on all platforms at 10 AM Pacific on June 12th 2022!  Explore a cold and hostile Norse-inspired archipelago in ARK's newest official community map, featuring four new creatures for you to collect! Fjordur contains over 140 square kilometers of new biomes, new challenges, and rewarding discoveries!|Traverse a fantastical multi-layered wonderland with a frosty Nordic theme. Four unique islands, Vardiland, Vannaland, Bolbjord and Balheimr, and the mystical realms; Jotunheim, Vanaheim, and Asgard, offer elaborate cave systems resplendent with Scandinavian ruins and vast monolithic entrances. Take a well-trodden hallowed path to pay respects at the immense and sacred world tree, Yggdrasil. Vestiges of ancient dwarven kingdoms harken to a lost era, the remnants of which lend an awe-inspiring history to the world of Fjordur. This beautiful and mythic world invites Survivors to a deeply forested land of bygone wonder and exploration!|Fjordur is the second community map released with completely new creatures, and the second to include another creature chosen by the ARK community. Unleash a tank-like fury from atop the saddle of your Andrewsarchus, explore with the Fjordhawk, ARK's newest shoulder pet companion, travail the icy landscape accompanied by your frosty Fenrir, or drain your enemies' and foes' lifeforce with the Desmodus!|Twitter: twitter.com/survivetheark|Discord: discord.com/invite/playark|Reddit: reddit.com/r/playark|Instagram: instagram.com/survivetheark|Twitch: twitch.tv/survivetheark|Steam: steamcommunity.com/app/346110|Youtube: youtube.com/survivetheark|Facebook: facebook.com/survivetheark

title: Street Fighter 6 High Level Gameplay (Hardest CPUs)
description: At Summer Game Fest, we pit two rank 8 CPU's against each other to duke it out in Street Fighter 6 at the highest level. |You'll get to see matches with Jamie, Ryu, Chun Li and Luke which were the four playable characters at Summer Game Fest's Play Days.  We got a chance to record these high level CPU matches at the Capcom booth for your viewing pleasure. Watch some of these intense combos from the 4 characters! |You'll get to see the new Drive System in play as well. With the Drive Gauge you are able to perform five different techniques that can enhance your offense or defense. Drive Impact is a powerful strike that can absorb an opponentâ€™s incoming attack and can lead to a wall splat. Drive Parry is used to repel your opponentâ€™s attack and refill your Drive Gauge. Additionally, you can cancel your Drive Parry or normal attack into a Drive Rush to quickly close in on your opponent. Overdrive Arts are similar to EX Moves from previous Street Fighter games that strengthen your Special Moves. Finally the fifth option in the new Drive System, is Drive Reversal which allows you to perform a counterattack to get you out of difficult situations. |You'll also get to see some critical arts in play as well.|#summergamefest #sf6 #streetfighter6

title: New labelling requirements for ground meat in Canada drawing criticism
description: In the coming weeks, Canadians may see new labels on packages of ground meat at the grocery store.|Health Canada says nutrition symbols will now be required on those packages for foods high in sodium, sugars, or saturated fats.|Many products will be exempt, but ground meat won't be one of them. title: Vishy Anand on Norway Chess 2022- phenomenal games, missed chances, premature resignation and more!
description: At 52 years of age, no one expected Vishy Anand to play the way he did at Norway Chess 2022. He finished third behind Carlsen and Mamedyarov, ahead of Giri, Radjabov, MVL, So and many strong players. In this interview we speak to Vishy about the critical moments in his games and how he dealt with them. title: China will fight to the very end to stop Taiwan independence: Defence minister | Shangri-La Dialogue
description: China will "fight to the very end" to stop Taiwan from declaring independence, Chinese Defence Minister Wei Fenghe said in a speech at the Shangri-La Dialogue on Sunday (Jun 12). |"We will fight at all cost and we will fight to the very end. This is the only choice for China," General Wei said.|His speech came a day after US Secretary of Defense Lloyd Austin said China was becoming "more coercive and aggressive" in its approach to its territorial claims in the region.|On Sunday, General Wei said Beijing firmly rejects the US' "smearing accusations and even threats" against China.|Global affairs should be handled through consultation by all stakeholders instead of being dictated by just one country or a small group of countries, he said, adding: "No one or no group of countries should impose its will on others or bully others under the guise of multilateralism."|General Wei said the United States' Indo-Pacific strategy is an attempt to build an exclusive small group in the name of a free and open Pacific to "hijack countries in the region and target one specific country". It is a strategy to "create conflict and confrontation to contain and encircle others", he said.|READ more: https://cna.asia/3NLIlsq|Subscribe to our channel here: https://cna.asia/youtubesub ||||Subscribe to our news service on Telegram: https://cna.asia/telegram||||Follow us:||CNA: https://cna.asia||CNA Lifestyle: http://www.cnalifestyle.com ||Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/channelnewsasia||Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/channelnewsasia||Twitter: https://www.twitter.com/channelnewsasia

title: Justin Thomas shoots 7-under 63 | Round 3 | RBC Canadian | 2022
description: In the third round of the 2022 RBC Canadian Open, Justin Thomas fired a 7-under, bogey-free 63, climbing into a tie for third at 9-under overall, and is two shots back after 54 holes.|SUBSCRIBE to PGA TOUR now: http://pgat.us/vBxcZSh||||Rory McIlroy will look to defend his title this weekend, as the PGA TOUR returns to St Georgeâ€™s Golf and Country Club for the RBC Canadian Open. The course last hosted the tournament in 2010 when Carl Pettersson was victorious. Three years ago, Northern Irishman McIlroy beat the course record to claim victory finishing seven shots clear of second place. World No. 1 Scottie Scheffler will be looking for a fifth victory this year, having narrowly missed out on another first place finish last weekend in a tense playoff with Sam Burns at the Charles Schwab Challenge. Other notable players teeing up include 2022 PGA Championship winner Justin Thomas, THE PLAYERS Championship winner Cameron Smith as well as Tony Finau, Justin Rose and Tyrell Hatton.||||Check out https://www.pgatour.com for complete coverage along with all the latest news, scoring, and stats!||||Follow PGA TOUR online:||Instagram: https://instagram.com/pgatour/  ||Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PGATour  ||Twitter: https://twitter.com/PGATOUR||TikTok: https://tiktok.com/@pgatour||SoundCloud: https://soundcloud.com/pgatour||||Sign up for exclusive coverage - http://www.pgatourlive.com||PGA TOUR Superstore - http://www.pgatoursuperstore.com/

Heâ€™s placed succulents in a section of the wall which only has four hours of sun per day.  |Eric also has some â€œminiâ€ green walls in the garden. title: 'Won't flinch': U.S returns fire after China threatened war over Taiwan
description: US Secretary of Defence Lloyd Austin stressed American support for Taiwan on Saturday, suggesting at Asia's premier defence forum that recent Chinese military activity around the self-governing island threatens to change the status quo. Speaking at the Shangri-La Dialogue in Singapore, Austin noted a â€œsteady increase in provocative and destabilising military activity near Taiwan,â€ including almost daily military flights near the island by the People's Republic of China. Taiwan and China split during a civil war in 1949, but China claims the island as its own territory and has not ruled out using military force to take it. Watch this video for more.|#taiwan #usa #china #xijinping #biden #lloydaustin #pacific #war

title: Women's Boulder final || Brixen 2022
description: Following back-to-back World Cups last month in Salt Lake City, Utah, USA, the International Federation of Sport Climbing (IFSC) World Cup Series 2022 continues this weekend with the fifth instalment of the season. Returning to Europe, the Italian town of Brixen is set to play host to the next IFSC Boulder World Cup events, from 10 to 12 June 2022. |The IFSC Boulder World Cup Brixen 2022 is the first IFSC competition to take place in Italy since the IFSC Youth World Championships Arco 2019, as well as the first IFSC World Cup to be held in the country since 2018. Moreover, this is the first time that Brixen has hosted an IFSC World Cup, having previously welcomed only continental Sport Climbing competitions including the IFSC Europe Cup this May.|More news: https://bit.ly/3ivwb9v|Subscribe: https://bit.ly/3oveCdv

Podremos con estos desafÃ­os en el tiempo que queda.|Se trata de obras de inversiÃ³n pÃºblica que administrarÃ¡ la SecretarÃ­a de Marina, porque queremos que esa dependencia defienda los bienes del pueblo y de la naciÃ³n. |El Gobierno de la Cuarta TransformaciÃ³n procura el desarrollo econÃ³mico horizontal y equilibrado y fomenta el crecimiento en las regiones sur y sureste del paÃ­s a fin de revertir el rezago que generÃ³ el modelo neoliberal.|MÃ¡s informaciÃ³n: https://bit.ly/3xfoJGg|Sigue las actividades del presidente de MÃ©xico: |Sitio web:|http://presidente.gob.mx|YouTube:|https://www.youtube.com/lopezobrador|Facebook:|https://facebook.com/lopezobrador.org.mx|Twitter:|https://twitter.com/lopezobrador_|Instagram:|https://www.instagram.com/lopezobrador/|Telegram: |https://t.me/PresidenteAMLO|Spotify:|https://spoti.fi/2C7jUmx

Luhansk governor Serhiy Haidai has said that the Azot chemical plant in Severodonetsk is now under Ukrainian control. title: Bulldozers roll in U.P's Saharanpur as Yogi vows to punish violence accused after Prophet protests
description: In view of the violence during protests in different parts of Uttar Pradesh on  Friday, Chief Minister Yogi Adityanath told officials to take stern action and set an example so that no one dares to disturb peace in the state. Amid this, Bulldozers rolled in Saharanpur and razed properties of those involved in violence, On Friday, people pelted stones at policemen in Prayagraj and Saharanpur and protests broke out after Friday prayers in at least four other cities in Uttar Pradesh over a Nupur Sharma's recent remarks on the Prophet. Watch this video for more.|#up #uttarpradesh #bulldozer #yogiadityanath #prophet #yogiadityanath #saharanpur

title: Bulldozer action in U.P? Yogi's aide hints at razing properties of Prophet insult violence accused
description: A day after widespread violence broke out in several UP cities against Prophet insult, CM Yogi Adityanath's media advisor has put out a cryptic tweet, hinting at bulldozer action against accused. Mrityunjay Kumar wrote: 'Remember, every Friday is followed by a Saturday' and posted a picture of bulldozer along with the tweet text. Meanwhile, CM Yogi has held a meeting with top bureaucrats and directed authorities to act against the violence accused.|#UP #YogiAdityanath #Violence #Bulldozer #MritynjayKumar

title: Homemade Naan Recipe

title: Diduga untuk Dana Operasional, Polisi Sita Uang Miliaran Rupiah Milik Khilafatul Muslimin Lampung!
description: LAMPUNG, KOMPAS.TV - Proses penyelidikan kasus Ormas Khilafatul Muslimin saat ini terus dilakukan.||||Setelah menangkap pimpinan tertinggi Khilafatul Muslimin, Abdul Qadir Baraja, kali ini tim gabungan Direskrimum Polda Metro Jaya menangkap dua tokoh penting di Khilafatul Muslimin di Bandar Lampung.||||Selain menangkap dua tokoh Khilafatul Muslimin, polisi juga menggeledah Kantor Pusat Khilafatul Muslimin di Lampung.||||Dalam penggeledahan itu, polisi membawa sejumlah barang bukti dari Kantor Khilafatul Muslimin; di antaranya sejumlah dokumen dan uang miliaran rupiah.||||Uang itu diduga sebagai dana operasional Khilafatul Muslimin.||||Sebelumnya, Pimpinan Tertinggi Khilafatul Muslimin, Abdul Qadir Baraja, ditangkap atas dugaan makar dan penyebaran berita bohong pada Selasa (7/6) lalu.||||Saat itu, polisi menemukan sejumlah buku terkait ISIS dan NII di  Kantor Pusat Khilafatul Muslimin.||||Temuan barang bukti itu kini didalami penyidik terkait paham ajaran yang rutin disebarkan oleh Khilafatul Muslimin.||||Lantas, sejauh mana pihak otoritas mengetahui asal-usul dan peruntukkan dana miliaran rupiah di Kantor Khilafatul Muslimin itu?||||Untuk membahasnya, sudah bergabung di Kompas Malam, Direktur Pencegahan Badan Nasional Penanggulangan Terorisme (BNPT), Akhmad Nurwakhid.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298123/diduga-untuk-dana-operasional-polisi-sita-uang-miliaran-rupiah-milik-khilafatul-muslimin-lampung

title: How united on Ukraine is the EU? | DW News
description: Unity in the face of aggression is a sentiment EU member states stressed over and over again when Russian troops first invaded Ukraine. But that unity developed cracks when it came to the specifics - how to punish Putin and his allies? How to best support Ukraine? Now, over a hundred days into the war, the positions keep drifting apart, as Christine Mhundwa reports.|The European Commission chief Ursula von der Leyen made a surprise visit to Kyiv for talks with Ukraine's President Volodymyr Zelenskyy.|They focused on Ukraine's bid to join the European Union. Kyiv submitted its membership application back in March. Brussels is set to publish its final assessment next week. Von der Leyen says the commission is working all-out to facilitate the process.|Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/user/deutschewelleenglish?sub_confirmation=1|For more news go to: http://www.dw.com/en/|Follow DW on social media:|â–ºFacebook: https://www.facebook.com/deutschewellenews/|â–ºTwitter: https://twitter.com/dwnews|â–ºInstagram: https://www.instagram.com/dwnews|FÃ¼r Videos in deutscher Sprache besuchen Sie: https://www.youtube.com/dwdeutsch|#EU #Ukraine #Russia

title: Signalis - Release Date Trailer | PS4 Games
description: SIGNALIS - Release Date Trailer |A classic survival horror experience set in a dystopian future where humanity has uncovered a dark secret. Unravel a cosmic mystery, escape terrifying creatures, and scavenge the corners of an off-world government facility as Elster, a technician Replika searching for her lost dreams.|Searching for dreams inside of a nightmare|Awaken from slumber and explore a surreal retrotech world as Elster, a technician Replika searching for her lost partner and her lost dreams. Discover terrifying secrets, challenging puzzles, and nightmarish creatures in a tense and melancholic experience of cosmic dread and classic psychological survival horror.|Fatal exception|SIGNALIS is set in a dystopian future where humanity has colonized the solar system, and the totalitarian regime of Eusan maintains an iron grip through aggressive surveillance and propaganda. Humanoid androids known as Replikas live among the populace, acting as workers, civil servants, and Protektors alongside the citizens they are designed to resemble.|The story of SIGNALIS begins as a Replika named Elster awakens from cryostasis in a wrecked vessel. Now stranded on a cold planet, she sets out on a journey into depths unknown.|Classic survival horror gameplay|Experience fear and apprehension as you encounter strange horrors, carefully manage scarce resources, and seek solutions to challenging riddles.|Cold and distant places|Explore the dim corners of a derelict spaceship, delve into the mysterious fate of the inhabitants of a doomed facility, and seek what lies beneath.|A dream about dreaming|Discover an atmospheric science-fiction tale of identity, memory, and the terror of the unknown and unknowable, inspired by classic cosmic horror and the works of Stanley Kubrick, Hideaki Anno, and David Lynch.|A striking vision|Wander a brutalist nightmare driven by fluid 3D character animations, dynamic lights and shadows, and complex transparency effects, complemented by cinematic sci-fi anime storytelling.|#ps4games

title: What Navy Recruits Go Through In Boot Camp | Boot Camp | Business Insider
description: We got an inside look at the United States Navy's 10-week basic training program. Chief video correspondent Graham Flanagan spent five days inside Recruit Training Command Great Lakes, where he observed different companies at various stages of training at the facility located about 35 miles north of Chicago.|Recruits must pass a physical assessment and a swim qualification before they train in seamanship, firefighting, and weapons training. They're also exposed to tear gas inside a confidence chamber where they learn to correctly wear gas masks.|Training culminates with â€œBattle Stationsâ€ an all-night event that takes place on a mock Navy destroyer ship designed by companies who have created theme park attractions for Walt Disney World. title: Yemen's dirty war | DW Documentary
description: At least 370,000 people have already died in the Yemen conflict, while millions have been displaced. The United Nations ranks the bloody proxy war and its effects as the world's worst humanitarian crisis.|The conflict in Yemen, in the south of the Arabian Peninsula, has been going on for years, and has recently seen renewed intensity. In January, an airstrike by the Saudi-led coalition on a prison in the north of the country killed at least 70 people and left hundreds injured. The war has now effectively divided Yemen in two. Its causes are more than just economic and religious ones. It is seen as a proxy war between Saudi Arabia and Iran. At stake are regional dominance, untapped oil reserves and access to the Red Sea, including the all-important Suez Canal. |Sanaâ€™a, the erstwhile Yemeni capital, is now considered one of the most inaccessible places on the planet. For the past six years, the city has been controlled by a Houthi political and military movement calling itself "Ansar Allah." But Saudi Arabia and the United Arab Emirates view the Houthi rebels, who belong to the Zaydism branch of Islam, as heretics who pose a threat to Wahhabism. Using weapons provided by the West, they have relentlessly bombarded the north of the country. Meanwhile, a strict embargo is starving the population, with some 400,000 children at risk of death from famine.|#documentary #dwdocumentary |______|DW Documentary gives you knowledge beyond the headlines. title: [TOP 3 NEWS] Jokowi Kangen Relawan, Jenazah Eril ke Indonesia, 2 Orang Khilafatul Muslimin Ditangkap
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV -  Berita Pertama, Presiden Joko Widodo gelar silaturahmi bersama relawan tim 7 di E-Convention Ancol, Jakarta Utara. Dalam acara itu, relawan membacakan panca dharma, yang salah satu poinnya bersama Jokowi pada 2024. Saat memberikan sambutan Jokowi mengaku sudah kangen kepada relawan pendukungnya. Apalagi sejak berakhirnya pemilihan presiden 2019 lalu, hingga indonesia harus menghadapi pandemi Covid-19.||||Baca Juga Jenazah Eril Diterbangkan Satu Pesawat dengan Ridwan Kamil di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298077/jenazah-eril-diterbangkan-satu-pesawat-dengan-ridwan-kamil||||Berita Kedua, Jenazah anak sulung Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil Emmeril Kahn Mumtadz akan dimakamkan di lahan milik keluarga yang berada di Cimaung, Kabupaten Bandung, Jawa Barat. Jenazah putra sulung gubernur jawa barat ridwan kamil, diterbangkan dari Swiss pada Sabtu pagi. Menurut Direktur Perlindungan WNI Kementerian Luar Negeri Judha Nugraha, jenazah eril diterbangkan satu pesawat dengan Ridwan kamil.||||Baca Juga Tangkap 2 Anggota, Polisi Juga Sita Uang Miliaran Rupiah dari Khilafatul Muslimin Lampung! di https://www.kompas.tv/article/298086/tangkap-2-anggota-polisi-juga-sita-uang-miliaran-rupiah-dari-khilafatul-muslimin-lampung||||Berita Ketiga, Kericuhan sempat terjadi saat Polda Metro Jaya dan Polresta Bandar Lampung membawa dua anggota kelompok tersebut berinisial AA dan IM. Dari hasil penggeledahan juga turut diamankan uang miliaran rupiah dari dalam brankas, yang diduga sebagai dana operasional serta dokumen dan struktur organisasi. 2 orang tersebut beserta barang bukti yang disita langsung dibawa ke Mapolda Metro Jaya untuk dilakukan pemeriksaan lebih lanjut.||||Video Editor: Agung|| ||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298112/top-3-news-jokowi-kangen-relawan-jenazah-eril-ke-indonesia-2-orang-khilafatul-muslimin-ditangkap

title: I Cut Off a Rhino's Horn.
description: Donate now. Help us reach our goal of $1,000,000 and make conservation history. |Rhinos are dying. Poaching, habitat loss, and genetic fragmentation have collectively pushed rhino populations to the brink of extinction. Illegal and deadly horn poaching is far and wide the greatest threat to rhinos. To deter this gruesome practice often calls for extreme measuresâ€¦ like chainsawing off a rhinoâ€™s horn.  |This is the reality of the fight to save rhinos. |In this episode, Coyoteâ€™s on-location at the Kariega Game Reserve shadowing the incredible Dr. William Fowlds as he conducts two important veterinary rhino procedures. Itâ€™s a race against the clock to protect these vanishing giants before theyâ€™re lost forever. |We have a plan to put things back on track. Brave Wilderness is partnering with Kariega Game Reserve, Global Conservation Force and Bear Grylls to Save The Horns.  |Learn more at savethehorns.com |A massive thank you to Kariega Game Reserve, Dr. William Fowlds, Global Conservation Force, and to YOU for doing your part. |PLEASE DO NOT ATTEMPT TO REENACT OR RECREATE ANY EVENTS OR SCENESâ€¯ FROM OUR VIDEOS. THE ANIMALS, INSECTS, PLANT LIFE, AND TERRAIN FEATURED INâ€¯ OUR VIDEOS CAN BE DANGEROUS AND CAN POSE A SIGNIFICANT RISK OF INJURY ORâ€¯ DEATH. The Brave Wilderness hosts and crew are professionally trained and routinelyâ€¯ receive assistance from wildlife experts, guides, and safety personnel when filming toâ€¯ ensure the safety of our crew and all wildlife. No animals were harmed or removed fromâ€¯ their natural habitat while making this video. Brave Wilderness has obtained permissionâ€¯ to film in each location featured in this video.

title: Russian Su-25 warhorse survives Ukraine missiles, returns safely despite damage
description: Su-25, the ultimate warrior, is terrorizing targets from above; Ukrainians finding it tough to take down the jet. Yet another Sukhoi Su-25 was able to return to base safely, despite being damaged by Ukrainian MANPADS. Heavily armored airframe & armored fuel tanks, pilot encased in a protective, bathtub-style cockpit. The 'Frogfoot' possesses 10 wing pylons to carry a variety of missiles, as well dumb & laser-guided bombs. title: An Epic Flight - Flying the Ilyushin IL-76 Cargo Transporter to Iraq
description: This week, I flew on SilkWay Ilyushin IL-76 transporter from Baku to Erbil, Iraq. The flight was completely different from the Western conventional airplane.  It took a strong team of 5 men to operate including 2 pilots, a. flight engineer, a radio controller and a navigator. The flight also carries a loadmaster and 2 technicians.|Before takeoff, the captain and loadmaster briefly introduced the cockpit and the cargo cabin. Inside the cabin, it has a crane system and ramp system able to lower to load without infrastructure. This particular IL-76TD-90 has new stage 4 noise compliant engines (Perm PS90 engines) instead of the older and noisier Soloviev D-30 engines.|Our flight took 2.5 hours from Baku to Erbil. After dropping off the cargo, we flew back to Baku empty. The view from the navigator seat through the glass nose was amazing. Watch the full video of the entire IL-76 flight and cargo operation.|The Ilyushin Il-76 is a multi-purpose, fixed-wing, four-engine turbofan strategic airlifter designed by the Soviet Union's Ilyushin design bureau. It was first planned as a commercial freighter in 1967. For more information, visit: https://www.silkwayairlines.com/fleet/il-76td-1/|Cover Image: Andreas Kolbe

title: Presiden Jokowi soal Capres 2024: Ketika Saatnya Tepat, Saya Akan Tanya "Siapa?"
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV - Presiden Joko Jokowi Widodo menghadiri Silaturahmi relawan di kawasan Ancol, Jakarta Utara.||||Silaturahmi bertajuk "2024 Satu Sikap Bersama Jokowi".||||Dalam sambutannya, Presiden menjelaskan soal situasi pandemi Covid-19 dan dampak perang Rusia-Ukraina, juga situasi harga bahan pokok.||||Sementara soal Capres 2024, Jokowi akan menunggu momen yang tepat untuk bicara, sambil mendengarkan suara dari "akar rumput".||||Sebelumnya, Presiden Joko Widodo juga mengomentari teriakan, "Lanjutkan!" yang dilantangkan oleh Menteri Investasi/Kepala BKPM, Bahlil Lahadalia, saat menutup pidatonya dalam acara ulang tahun Himpunan Pengusaha Muda Indonesia.||||Bahlil menjelaskan yang dimaksud adalah melanjutkan program pembangunan.||||Dalam pidato di acara perayaan 50 tahun Himpunan Pengusaha Muda Indonesia, Presiden Joko Widodo juga mengingatkan untuk hati-hati menyebutkan kata "Lanjutkan", apalagi menurutnya saat ini merupakan tahun politik.||||Jokowi menegaskan yang perlu dilanjutkan adalah hasil kerja pemerintahannya saat ini.||||Presiden Joko Widodo kembali menegaskan menolak gagasan perpanjangan jabatan Presiden.||||Menurutnya, yang terpenting adalah melanjutkan pembangunan yang telah berjalan saat ini, oleh siapa pun presidennya.||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298092/presiden-jokowi-soal-capres-2024-ketika-saatnya-tepat-saya-akan-tanya-siapa

title: Jenazah Eril Diterbangkan Satu Pesawat dengan Ridwan Kamil
description: JAKARTA, KOMPAS.TV  Jenazah putra sulung Gubernur Jawa Barat Ridwan Kamil, diterbangkan dari Swiss pada Sabtu (11/6/2022) pagi waktu Swiss. ||||Menurut Direktur Perlindungan WNI Kementerian Luar Negeri Judha Nugraha Jenazah Eril diterbangkan satu pesawat dengan Ridwan Kamil. ||||Pak Ridwan Kamil take off pada pukul 10.10 waktu Swiss atau pukul 15.10 WIB. Jenazah satu flight dengan Pak Ridwan Kamil,"kata Direktur Perlindungan WNI Kementerian Luar Negeri Judha Nugraha, Sabtu (11/6/2022).||||Baca Juga Momen Atalia Praratya Tinjau Langsung Persiapan Pemakaman Eril di https://www.kompas.tv/article/297966/momen-atalia-praratya-tinjau-langsung-persiapan-pemakaman-eril||||Ridwan Kamil pun dijadwalkan tiba di Indonesia Minggu (12/6/2022) sore. ||||"Bapak Ridwan Kamil dan jenazah direncanakan akan tiba di Bandara Soekarno Hatta pada hari Minggu, pukul 15.45 Waktu Indonesia Barat," lanjut Judha. ||||Mewakili Kementerian Luar Negeri, Judha juga turut mendoakan proses kepulangan jenazah Eril lancar hingga nanti prosesi pemakaman. ||||Video Editor: Agung||||Artikel ini bisa dilihat di :  https://www.kompas.tv/article/298077/jenazah-eril-diterbangkan-satu-pesawat-dengan-ridwan-kamil
